(2, '399 El Geish Road Four Seasons Hotel Alexandria at San Stefano, Alexandria 21599 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'Fresca Mediterranean Bistro and Lounge welcomes you with an easy-going atmosphere and warm hospitality that makes you feel like you?re at home with friends and family. Chef Alessio Pitzalis and his team have curated a fresh menu featuring favourite breakfast items, a live pizzaiolo counter and iconic dishes from the Mediterranean coast.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/28/5a/9c/dd/fresca-four-seasons-alexandria.jpg', 'Fresca, Four Seasons Alexandria at San Stefano', '4.5', 'http://www.fourseasons.com/alexandria/dining/restaurants/fresca/', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(3, '14th of May Bridge Road Inside Hilton Alexandria Green Plaza, Alexandria 21615 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'Massala Zone Indian Restaurant overlooking the outdoor swimming pool at Hilton Alexandria Green Plaza introduces an exquisite Indian menu. Using fresh high quality ingredients carefully cooked and blended with passion to create TOP INDIAN dishes, served in a cozy modern atmosphere. Open daily from 5 pm until 11 pm', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/18/15/fe/30/massala-zone-indian-restaurant.jpg', 'Massala Zone Indian Restaurant', '5', 'https://www3.hilton.com/en/hotels/egypt/hilton-alexandria-green-plaza-ALYGPHI/dining/index.html', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(4, '544 El-Gaish Rd, Alexandria 21599 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'Relax in a traditional Restaurant and admire the sweeping sea views while enjoying a coffee, croissant, cake, pastries, pizzas and light meals.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/12/20/6b/c8/la-gourmandise-plates.jpg', 'La Gourmandise Restaurant and Cafe', '5', 'http://www.lagourmandiseegypt.com/News.aspx?N=2', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(5, 'Hilton Alexandria Green Plaza, 14th of May Bridge Road, Smouha, Alexandria 21615 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'An upscale Italian restaurant with a contemporary elegance and sophistication. Roberto?s spirit carries through the entire dining experience with a core philosophy of being Italian in all possible facets. Working with only the best of Italian products and produce, enables the kitchen to be true to one of the most recognizable aspects of the cuisine.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/0f/38/bb/33/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', '5', 'http://www3.hilton.com/en/hotels/egypt/hilton-alexandria-green-plaza-ALYGPHI/index.html', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(6, '544 El Geish Road, Sidi Bishr Sidi Bishr, Alexandria 21611 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'Cast away your stress and enjoy a drink or favorite cocktail in our Cigar Bar. Our contemporary bar is serving light meals, snacks and refreshments all day. The bar is renowned for the wide selection of famous cigar brands.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/19/79/01/ad/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'The Cigar Bar', '5', 'http://www3.hilton.com/en/hotels/egypt/hilton-alexandria-corniche-ALYACHI/index.html', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(7, '544 El-Gaish Rd, Sidi Beshr Bahri, Montaza 1 Hilton Alexandria Corniche, Alexandria 21611 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'Sahar El Laialy Lebanese Restaurant at Hilton Alexandria Corniche invites you to experience the best of theatre and dining in an immersive culinary journey following Le Petit Chef, the world\'s smallest chef! Enjoy an unforgettable experience that will capture your imagination!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/28/87/13/ba/caption.jpg', 'Le Petit Chef - Alexandria', '5', 'http://lepetitchef.com/alexandria-hilton-lpc1', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(8, '399 El Geish Road Four Seasons Hotel Alexandria at San Stefano, Alexandria 21599 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'Whether it?s a date night or simply craving for pasta, Stefano?s serves up authentic Southern Italian cuisine made by our Italian Chef Giuseppe Pucciarelli in a warm and intimate setting. With an open kitchen, chic decor, and warm Italian hospitality to keep you coming back for more.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/19/87/c1/2b/stefano-s.jpg', 'Stefano\'s Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.fourseasons.com/alexandria/dining/restaurants/stefano_s_restaurant/', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(9, 'L Bay , Fort Qaitbay area , Bahary Qaitbay Area , 2nd floor., Alexandria 21599 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'SeaSside is located at the historic area of Fort Qaitbay and overlooking the wonderful Eastern Marina make it the best sea view in town and the most experienced chefs give you joy and happiness while eating fresh and tasty seafood as well as pastas', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/19/36/94/37/the-best-sea-view-in.jpg', 'SeaSide', '4.5', 'http://g.page/SeaSideegypt?share', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(10, 'Hussein Bek Wali, Hannovill, Alexandria Governorat, Alexandria Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'fooshi is an Egyptian fast food restaurant chain. Headquartered in Alexandria, Egypt, that primarily sells grilled and fried fish & seafood with a variety of sauces, fooshi is owned by OuDek.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/28/bb/44/89/shrimp-sandwich-with.jpg', 'fooshi', '4.5', 'https://fooshi.oudek.net/', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(11, '399 El Geish Road Four Seasons Hotel Alexandria at San Stefano, Alexandria 21599 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'Take a seat overlooking the Mediterranean to enjoy plates of hot and cold mezzeh and authentic Lebanese and Syrian favourites, surrounded by elaborate woodworking, gilded ceilings and views of the Mediterranean, in our elegant formal restaurant.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/19/87/ba/94/byblos-entrance.jpg', 'Byblos Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.fourseasons.com/alexandria/dining/restaurants/byblos_restaurant/', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(12, 'Montaza Palace Gardens In front of Montazah Water Sports Club., Alexandria 21599 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'At Zanilli\'s, we enjoy making and serving food, delighting every guest with an unforgettable experience is our purpose aiming for your satisfaction. We prepare our food fresh every day in our kitchens using the highest quality ingredients serving from sandwiches, salads, pasta to fillet and many more through our branches.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1b/11/2c/9b/montaza.jpg', 'Zanilli\'s Cafe & More Montazah', '3.5', 'http://www.zanillis.com/Zanillis_Home.aspx', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(13, '83 El Geish Rd Ramleh Station, Alexandria 21599 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'Fine Dining Restaurant,cafe,Bar & Grill,Breakfast,French, Greek and Mediterranean,Seafood, Tapas Bars and Vegetarian.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/01/a0/bf/a7/calithea.jpg', 'Calithea Restaurant', '4', 'http://www.calithea-alex.com', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(14, '16 Midan Saad Zaghloul Cecil Hotel, Alexandria 21599 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'Telephone 03 487 7173', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/44/df/26/20170123-164219-largejpg.jpg', 'China House', '4', 'http://www.elmenus.com/alexandria/restaurants/china-house-4274/san-stefano-5985', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(15, 'Corniche Road Sheraton Montazah Hotel, Ground Floor, Alexandria 21923 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'La Mamma Restaurant brings the robust flavors & authentic cooking traditions of Italy to you! La Mamma Menu offers a deliciously diverse array of Italian gourmet specialties with the finest ingredients along with an exceptional service all days. We promise you a memorable culinary experience that they will never forget in a sophisticated clean surroundings and a cozy atmosphere. Open for lunch and dinner.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/2a/7b/07/00/la-mamma-restaurant.jpg', 'La Mamma', '4', 'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/alysi-sheraton-montazah-hotel/dining/', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(16, '43 Safia Zaghlol Street, Alexandria 21599 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'Bar & lounge & restaurant', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/28/fa/ed/ee/caption.jpg', 'Nyx Bar & Lounge', '5', 'https://instagram.com/nyx.bar.egy?igshid=nmnmnjawnzg=', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(17, 'No. 22 Fouad Street, Alexandria 21599 Egypt', 'Alexandria', 'Our dishes are made fresh daily by our Chefs. We serve a wide variety of savoury baked potatoes, mouthwatering pastas and wholesome healthy salads.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/26/96/e2/f9/shrimp-red-sauce-pasta.jpg', 'Potasta', '5', 'http://potasta.com/en/', 4, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(18, 'Imam Al Daaeri, Aswan Egypt', 'Aswan', 'A Healthy Grill Restaurant with inside and outside seating facilities on the bank of the River Nile.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1d/67/be/07/the-new-menu-from-makani.jpg', 'Makani restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/MakaniAswanFB', 7, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(19, 'Movenpick Resort Aswan, Elephantine Island, Aswan Egypt', 'Aswan', 'The Mezze restaurant offers a variety of authentic a` la carte Egyptian food with an indoor and outdoor seating. It is located at the Elephantine wing with a stunning views, directly facing the Nile River, the Botanical Island, the Mausoleum of Aga Khan and the Tomb of the Nobles. Experience the lunch & dinner at historical city like never before!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1d/48/81/6a/mezze-restaurant.jpg', 'Mezze Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.movenpick.com/en/africa/egypt/aswan/resort-aswan/restaurants/restaurants/mezze-restaurant/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=local&utm_campaign=glocal+mezze-rest', 7, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(20, 'Elephantine Island, Aswan 81111 Egypt', 'Aswan', 'Traditional Nubian dining experience with a Jamaican twist. Waterfront views of Aswan. Close to public ferry boat ( good food makes good days) We are mix nubian jamaican Cafe and restaurant located in elephantine Island aswan one of the old nubian villages Family business me and my father and my mother and my sister\'s it was our dream to build that restaurant to help the nubian community Just come and enjoy the experience and you will never regret. Thanks', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/21/81/34/c4/aubergine-bachamel-tagin.jpg', 'King Jamaica Restaurant & Cafe', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/kingjamaica123/', 7, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(21, 'Elephantine Island Near The Ferry Boat Cross to Bob Marley guest house restaurant cafe, Aswan 81111 Egypt', 'Aswan', 'Fresh, home cooked meals. Chicken, beef, camel, pigeon, fish and vegetable tagine or barbecue. Fresh juices and Nubian Jabana coffee. Alcohol is available as well as many flavours of shisha. Amazing views of The Nile River and Aswan city from the colourfully decorated terrace. Friendly Nubian staff who speak English and Arabic. Nothing is too much trouble to make', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1c/e7/24/f6/bob-marley.jpg', 'Bob Marley Guest House & Restaurant & Cafe', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Bob-Marley-guest-house-restaurant-Cafe-113315303924185/?tsid=0.815301325616822&source=result', 7, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(22, 'Nag Gharb Siheil, Aswan 81511 Egypt', 'Aswan', 'Kato Dool Restaurant & Caf‚ is located at Kato Dool Wellness Resort. The open-air setup is designed to embrace nature through the opulent Nile views and lavish trees complemented with the vibrant and colourful architecture of the resort conveying the Nubian lifestyle.Healthy nutrition and succulent dishes from Egyptian cuisine are brought from the resort?s organic farm-to-table bringing a variety of delicious oriental, vegetarian and vegan dishes from Egyptian cuisine. For an extra dimension of culinary experience, guests can enjoy late lunch or arrange special events at Kato Dool Felucca and unwind on the Nile shores. Indulge in our Food & Beverages offerings and enjoy a remarkable local experience!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/28/6e/de/ef/rice-with-caroot.jpg', 'Kato Dool Restaurant & Cafe', '5', 'http://www.katodool.com', 7, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(23, 'Kornish Al Nile, Sheyakhah Thalethah, Qism, Aswan Egypt', 'Aswan', 'We do pizza, pasta, sandwich, min course, kids meal, waffle, crepe, all off could drinks & hot drinks', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/21/a6/f3/04/negresco-pasta.jpg', 'Sun Deck Restaurant & Coffee', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Sundeck09/?ref=page_internal', 7, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(24, 'Aswan Egypt', 'Aswan', 'an authentic Nubian restaurant and guesthouse that offers a spectacular view on the Nile river and great authentic Nubian food in a Nubian decoration . during your experience there you will be served by a Nubian waiter and you will find books about the Nubian culture in all languages that will give you an insight into the Nubian and Upper Egyptian culture.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/12/48/a3/ed/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Old Nubian Guest House and Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/OldNubianguesthouse/', 7, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(25, 'Bigeh Island, Aswan Egypt', 'Aswan', 'Nubian kitchen is rich with its recipes, but unfortunately these recipes are not commonly used right now among Nubians and started to disappear. Our aim was to establish a Nubian restaurant that provide only Nubian cuisine with old and new recipes. The restaurant is located in a premium location on an island overlooking the famous Philae temple.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/60/ac/b7/view-from-solaih-nubian.jpg', 'Solaih Nubian Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://solaih-nubian-restaurant.business.site', 7, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(26, 'Corniche El Nile Officer Club infront of palace of culture, Aswan 81511 Egypt', 'Aswan', 'Our restaurant welcomes its guests from all over the world to taste our fast and inexpensive Egyptian food.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/1b/73/b0/a6/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Alexandria kaman we kaman Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/alexandriakamanwekaman/?ref=page_internal', 7, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(27, 'Kornish Al Nile Al Raya Market, Aswan 1, Aswan 11812 Egypt', 'Aswan ', 'Havana Caf‚ visit us and change your mode with your friends In your second home Enjoy with your Very Special (Drink - Food - Ice .Cream)', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/27/b8/e6/4c/whatever-your-taste-in.jpg', 'Havana Cafe', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Aswanhavanacafe/', 7, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(28, '3 Cleopatra Street Heliopolis, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Tucked away in a quiet street of Korba, Heliopolis. Sachi is a restaurant and bar, that brings to the neighbourhood a much needed watering hole, whether you are in for a drink or for a proper meal. Sachi\'s elegant interior is very well distributed into lounge, bar, high tables and dining areas, and can accommodate up to 100 people on its busiest weekend nights. By Baky Hospitality', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/21/b8/e0/49/you-had-us-at-sushi.jpg', 'Sachi Heliopolis', '5', 'http://www.sachirestaurant.com', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(29, 'Ring Road Renaissance Cairo Mirage City Hotel, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Experience Chinese culinary art in unique surroundings, one of the world?s best cuisines. Discover our signature dishes including Beijing Duck and Dim Sum.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/29/69/12/02/chinoix-chinese-restaurant.jpg', 'Chinoix Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/CAIBR&scid=d42e66eb-35c2-4d9c-9219-ae39f3a2ca9f', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(30, 'JW Marriott Hotel, Ring Road, Mirage City Ring Road - Mirage City, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Savor the authentic flavors of Italy along with spirited live entertainment at JW Marriott Cairo\'s famous Italian kitchen. Enjoy mouth-watering pizzas and pastas and hearty hospitality within cozy surrounds.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0b/6f/5f/04/la-cucina.jpg', 'Cucina', '4.5', 'http://www.jwmarriottcairolife.com/restaurant/hotels/hotel-information/travel/caijw/dining/cucina', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(31, '1115 Corniche El Nile Ramses Hilton, Cairo 12344 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Indulge in Authentic Indian cuisine at Ramses Hilton. A wide range of individually prepared dishes including vegetarian options are available for you to choose from. Watch our Chefs from India delicately preparing Tandoori in the show cooking area while you savor a glass of lassi. Indian artwork, natural wood floors & atmospheric lighting complement the dining experience at Namaste.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1d/b3/b0/1c/namaste-indian-restaurant.jpg', 'Namaste Indian Restaurant', '5', 'http://www3.hilton.com/en/hotels/egypt/ramses-hilton-CAIRHTW/dining/index.html', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(32, '1113 Corniche El Nil St. Inside The Nile Ritz-Carlton, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'NOX opens its doors to the city?s movers and shakers for nights full of music, drinks and international surprises. The restaurant, lounge and bar offers global inspired sharing cuisine and crowd-pleasing hand crafted cocktails. A rooftop cosmopolitan night spot overlooking Cairo and the Nile in all its magical glory is the perfect place to see and be seen; enjoy a sleek ambiance, refined live performers and sophisticated DJ beats. Step Out Of NOX, cocktail in hand, feel the Nile breeze and gaze across the landmarks that define the city.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/16/7f/cb/4e/a-rooftop-lounge-with.jpg', 'Nox Restaurant, Bar & Lounge', '5', 'http://www.ritzcarlton.com/en/hotels/middle-east/cairo/dining/nox', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(33, '1113 Corniche El Nil The Nile Ritz Carlton -Second floor, Cairo 11221 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'In Italian it means ?alive?, this restaurant will give you the experience of rustic Italian cuisine in a modern setting where you will have the chance to go in a journey to the Italian countryside with the smell of homemade pizza and the largest Grappa selection in town.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/12/9e/5e/b3/rustic-and-contemporary.jpg', 'Vivo - The Nile Ritz-Carlton', '5', 'http://www.ritzcarlton.com/en/hotels/middle-east/cairo/dining/vivo', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(34, 'City Stars Mall Phase 1, Level 5, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Ni?anta??, named after an exclusive quarter on Istanbul?s European side, is Cairo\'s most exciting and stylish destination for Turkish cuisine. We offer atmospheric dining in a relaxing setting that attracts people from far and wide. The experience is unlike any other, from dishes to share with family and friends to the ceremonious flourish of a sealed terracotta cooking pot cut open at your table. Our cuisine offers so much to discover and delight in. ? Ni?anta?? is brought to you by International Food Academy', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/16/9e/c7/79/testi-kebab-tavuk-jarra.jpg', 'Nisantasi', '5', 'http://www.nisantasi.com.eg', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(35, '13 El Thawra St Korba, Heliopolis, Cairo 4460242 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'A marriage of two cultures; a tale of two homes. Modern Japanese fusion cuisine in the heart of Korba.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/25/9f/f1/01/a-tale-of-two-homes.jpg', 'Tokyo Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.instagram.com/tokyorestaurant_/?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y%3D', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(36, 'Omar Ibn EL Khattab St. Heliopolis InterContinental Cairo Citystars, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'A cozy Japanese restaurant serving the best of sushi and teppanyaki cuisine. Enjoy true Japanese atmosphere with a fish tank in the center of the restaurant. Enjoy the tasty food at either the sushi bar or one of the Japanese live cooking tables. Pick your favorite dish from our menus that are created by our Japanese chef Komatsu using top-quality fresh ingredients.Available Services: Credit card accepted, parking or valet services, alcohol, wireless Internet', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/94/92/46/shogun-aquarium.jpg', 'Shogun Japanese Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.ihg.com/intercontinental/hotels/gb/en/cairo/crohc/hoteldetail/dining?cm_mmc=GoogleMaps-_-IC-_-EG-_-CROHC', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(37, 'Hilton Cairo Heliopolis El Orouba Street, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'A lobby bar offering the funkiest cocktails, light bites, and snacks for both lunch and dinner. Rainbow also offers an A La Carte menu.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/17/86/23/f0/live-entertainment-and.jpg', 'Rainbow Bar', '5', 'http://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/caihehi-hilton-cairo-heliopolis/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(38, 'Hilton Cairo Heliopolis Uruba Street, Heliopolis, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Al Dabk‚: Mouthwatering Lebanese favorites, cooked on a charcoal grill using original ingredients and traditional cooking methods, mini BBQ at your table will simply keep your order as fresh as it can be. Open from 12:00 PM to Midnight. Family Friendly, Dress code: Smart Casual', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/16/5e/f8/12/al-dabke-authentic-atmosphere.jpg', 'AL Dabke', '5', 'http://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/caihehi-hilton-cairo-heliopolis/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(39, '1113 Corniche El Nil Street The Nile Ritz-Carlton, Downtown, Cairo 11221 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Casual, contemporary, all-day dining, featuring a kitchen theater with a wide selection of international and local favorites with the best Friday brunch in town.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/12/2b/04/22/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Culina', '5', 'http://ritzcarlton.com/cairo', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(40, 'Holiday Inn Cairo Maadi, 29 Corniche El Nil 29 Corniche El Nil, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'The perfect place for light bites and traditional afternoon tea in addition to delicious pastries, fresh bakeries and refreshing coffee in a modern setting.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/16/c3/9b/c3/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'ZEN Cafe & Lounge', '5', 'https://www.ihg.com/holidayinn/hotels/gb/en/cairo/crohi/hoteldetail/dining#', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(41, 'InterContinental Cairo Citystars Omar Bin Khattab Street, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Throughout the centuries, Egyptian cuisine has been part of the country?s heritage, history and romantic past. At Al Khal, the finest authentic Egyptian dishes and delights are brought to you in a classic setting with a modern twist and traditionally perfect service. Enjoy the tastes and flavours of the ages created for you. https://www.opentable.com/r/al-khal-reservations-cairo?restref=136452&lang=en-US', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/ae/b1/9a/al-khal-egyptian-dishes.jpg', 'Al Khal Egyptian Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.ihg.com/intercontinental/hotels/gb/en/cairo/crohc/hoteldetail/dining?cm_mmc=GoogleMaps-_-IC-_-EG-_-CROHC', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(42, 'Hilton Cairo Heliopolis Al Orouba Street, Heliopolis, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Enjoy a lavishing night-out at our authentic Italian restaurant; Leonardo and relish the sensation of the exquisite cuisine. Open from 12:00 PM to midnight. Family Friendly.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/19/84/57/83/leonardo-ristorante.jpg', 'Leonardo Ristorante', '5', 'http://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/caihehi-hilton-cairo-heliopolis/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(43, 'Hilton Cairo Heliopolis Al Orouba Street ,, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Named after the ?King of India?, Raj offers classic Indian cuisine with a modern touch. Savor the creations of tender meat and seafood directly from the hot embers of the tandoor, accompanied with soft, fresh, and hot naans, and Rotis. All in an inviting atmosphere complemented by an open kitchen for a live cooking experience. Family Friendly', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/16/88/3a/e0/renowned-biryani.jpg', 'Raj', '5', 'http://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/caihehi-hilton-cairo-heliopolis/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(44, '2005 B, Corniche El Nil Fairmont Towers Nile City - 2005 B, Corniche El Nil, Ramlet Beaulac, Cairo 2466 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Fairmont Nile City?s Pan-Asian fine dining restaurant offers a unique sharing concept with a signature twist of Asian cuisine for an unmatched culinary experience. Elegant interiors and stunning Nile views set the stage for a unique experience at Saigon Restaurant. The Lounge is the perfect location for an intimate get-together while enjoying some of the city\'s best live entertainment. Dress Code: Smart-Casual/Semi-Formal *Shorts and slippers are not allowed*', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/16/e4/af/1e/saigon-restaurant.jpg', 'Saigon Restaurant & Lounge', '5', 'http://www.fairmont.com/nile-city-cairo/dining/saigon-restaurant-and-lounge/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(45, '12 Ahmed Ragheb Street Garden City, Cairo 11519 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'The Blue Restaurant is a destination for modern Mediterranean and Italian cuisine. It offers authentically prepared dishes using only the finest imported meats, fresh seafood and other regional ingredients as you enjoy the ambiance of one of the city\'s most elegant dining venues. The restaurant serves all-day … la carte dishes, including antipasti, pastas and contemporary main dishes. Our dishes are full of the freshest flavours and the best-quality ingredients to form delicious recipes from the most talented Kempinski chefs.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/15/60/0c/5a/the-blue-restaurant-6.jpg', 'The Blue Restaurant & Grill', '5', 'http://www.kempinski.com/en/cairo/nile-hotel/dining/the-blue-restaurant-and-grill/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(46, '29 Cornish El Nil Maadi, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Indulge in a distinctive impeccable dining experience at Solis where we combine the signature atmosphere of the Nile view with the exquisite and authentic flavors of our Mediterranean cuisine dishes.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/43/d8/9b/solis-restaurant.jpg', 'Solis Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/SolisLounge/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(47, 'Hilton Cairo Heliopolis Uruba Street, Heliopolis, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Modern Chinese cuisine where taste surpasses expectation; partnered by three Teppanyaki grills, the restaurant menu reflects mainly Cantonese cuisine but not neglecting other reigns. Rich and tasteful black bean beef is the Chef\'s specialty making it difficult to resist. The authentic Chinese deco can only enhance the atmosphere and contribute to the fine dining experience. Dress code: Smart casual, Family Friendly', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/19/79/45/ed/noble-house-restaurant.jpg', 'Noble House', '5', 'http://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/caihehi-hilton-cairo-heliopolis/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(48, '1113 Corniche El Nil, Downtown, Cairo 11221 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'The Lobby Lounge, marked with its historic and contemporary masterpieces, the lounge offers a 24-hour dining destination in Cairo. The menu transforms throughout the day, suited for breakfast meetings and after-dinner nightcaps. Each Saturday, the lounge hosts the hotel?s signature Afternoon Tea served with a decadent chocolate display. Trio band every Thursday & Friday - Open 24 Hours.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1d/b1/19/d7/relaxed-yet-elegant-seating.jpg', 'Lobby Lounge', '5', 'http://www.ritzcarlton.com/en/hotels/middle-east/cairo/dining/lobby-lounge', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(49, '29 Corniche El Nil Holiday Inn Cairo, Maadi, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Join us at Scores Sports Bar & Restaurant, the newest sports bar in town, located at Holiday Inn Cairo Maadi - Egypt, enjoy dining & drinking overlooking the majestic Nile river', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/19/d8/1c/b8/scores-bar-upper-level.jpg', 'Scores Sports Bar & Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Scoressportsbar/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(50, 'Uruba Street, Cairo Egypt', 'Cairo', 'International buffet breakfast, featuring a wide selection of international and local main dishes, salad and dessert bar, seasonal fresh juices and much more. Family Friendly', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/16/7e/e7/10/my-kind-of-place.jpg', 'My Kind of Place', '5', 'http://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/caihehi-hilton-cairo-heliopolis/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(51, '12 Ahmed Ragheb Street Garden City, Cairo 11519 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Dine like a Sultan as attentive waiters present culinary treasures crafted by Turkish chefs. Discover Osmanly, the only nouveau Ottoman cuisine restaurant in town, the first treat you?ll receive is a brass pitcher of jasmine water to dip your hands and a warm towel to dry them off the perfect preparation for the delicacies ahead. The shared plate concept allows guests to try a variety of dishes as an introduction to the Middle East?s favourite cuisine. Open daily for lunch and dinner.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/15/5d/05/6c/osmanly-restaurant-1.jpg', 'Osmanly Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.kempinski.com/en/cairo/nile-hotel/dining/the-osmanly-restaurant/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(52, '1113 Corniche El Nil The Nile Ritz Carlton , ground Floor, Cairo 11221 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Flavors from around the Middle East are brought together at Bab El-Sharq. Set amid lush gardens with a view of the Egyptian Museum, the outdoor restaurant offers a traditional dining experience in the heart of Cairo. Mezze and signature dishes are paired with flavored shisha, live entertainment and broadcasts of major sporting events. Daily due Band, gulf singer & belly dancer.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/12/2b/14/2d/bab-el-sharq.jpg', 'Bab El-Sharq', '5', 'http://www.ritzcarlton.com/en/hotels/middle-east/cairo/dining/bab-el-sharq', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(53, 'Uruba Street El Orouba Street, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'A French Bistro serving the freshest coffees, breakfast, sandwiches, freshly baked cakes, salads, and pastries for dine-in or takeaway. Also, an A La Carte menu is available.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/19/73/e7/f3/le-marche.jpg', 'Le Marche', '5', 'http://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/caihehi-hilton-cairo-heliopolis/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(54, 'InterContinental Cairo Citystars Omar Ibn El Khattab St., Heliopolis, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Guests familiar with the flavours and spices of Lebanese cuisine will find them blended to perfection at Fayruz. for newcomers, let the famously friendly staff introduce you over lunch on the outdoor terrace or an exotic dinner show with live belly dancing. The interior is delightfully authentic and evocative.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/94/81/9f/kraides-mashwi-jumbo.jpg', 'Fayruz Lebanese Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.ihg.com/intercontinental/hotels/gb/en/cairo/crohc/hoteldetail/dining', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(55, '1191 Nile Corniche Inside Conrad Cairo, Cairo 11221 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Experience a culinary journey through South-East Asia at Kamala restaurant at Conrad Cairo Hotel & Casino. The stylish d‚cor and sophisticated mood lighting make this beautiful Cairo restaurant the perfect tranquil escape from city life.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/2a/25/08/af/kamala-s-kitchen.jpg', 'Kamala at Conrad Cairo', '5', 'http://conradhotels3.hilton.com/en/hotels/egypt/conrad-cairo-CAICICI/amenities/restaurants-kamala.html', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(56, 'InterContinental Cairo Semiramis Corniche El Nile, Garden City, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'The Night & Day is buffet dining a la minute at its finest. Chefs wait at their cooking stations to prepare fusion fare to order. The Asian station offers dim sum and Sushi, wok and Teppanyaki specialties, the grill station is where you\'ll go for Oriental and Tandoori items and the pasta and noodle station is just right for lighter bites. Salad, cold cut, carving and dessert stations complete the feast. Check out the Big Friday brunch. Open daily for breakfast, lunch and dinner.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0a/39/3c/12/the-appetizers-selection.jpg', 'Night & Day', '5', 'http://www.ihg.com/intercontinental/hotels/us/en/cairo/croha/hoteldetail', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(57, '16 Maarouf St., Champollion Rd Near To High Court House, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Koshary Abou Tarek is a prominent restaurant chain in Egypt, renowned for its signature dish, Koshary. The establishment\'s founder, Abou Tarek, began selling Koshary from a humble street cart in Cairo during the 1950s.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/2a/15/d1/52/koshary.jpg', 'Koshary Abou Tarek', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/koshariabotarek', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(58, 'Dusit Thani Lakeview Cairo Hotel, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'An all-new Multi Asian restaurant at the magnificent Dusit Thani LakeView Cairo TAO, first in the city featuring an impressively varied multi Asian style menu, reflects the best of Chinese, Indian, Thai and Japanese cuisines all run by native chefs, meant to fuel its guests and invigorate their senses. The combination of modern and elegant interiors combines a significant touch of each cuisine ingenious', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/27/e9/ea/a1/tao-restaurant.jpg', 'Tao', '5', 'http://taocairo.com/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(59, 'Ring Road, Cairo 11757 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'JW Marriott Cairo?s newest venue offers an unparalleled open air dining experience overlooking the magnificent greenery of the championship golf course and its shimmering lake.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/13/8f/0d/cc/enjoy-our-smart-menu.jpg', 'Plateau', '5', 'http://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/caijw-jw-marriott-hotel-cairo/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(60, 'Omar Ibn El Khattab St. InterContinental Cairo Citystars, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'From tasty snacks to a la carte meals to full buffet dinners with live cooking by top chefs, the Esplanade offers 24 hours variety without compromising on quality.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/05/a2/20/fc/esplanade-cafe-restaurant.jpg', 'Esplanade Cafe Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.ihg.com/intercontinental/hotels/gb/en/cairo/crohc/hoteldetail/dining?cm_mmc=GoogleMaps-_-IC-_-EG-_-CROHC', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(61, '58 Beirut Street, Heliopolis Heliopolis, Cairo 11200 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Chic Restaurant - Bar serving The Smokery?s Signature delicacies in the heart of Heliopolis with a large outdoor terrace in front of the bar. Ideal for Drinks or Dinner any day of the week.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/21/8f/21/dd/heliopolis.jpg', 'The Smokery Heliopolis', '5', 'http://www.thesmokeryrestaurants.com', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(62, 'Corniche El Nil Semiramis InterContinental Cairo, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Everything about the Birdcage is pure Thailand, from the exotic water feature at the door to the authentic etiquette displayed throughout your meal. What will really transport you across the continent; however, are the sizzling sounds and enticing aromas from the open kitchen, where Thai specialties such as garlic pepper shrimp, cashew chicken, and crispy rice with peanut sauce are created. Location: In the Semiramis InterContinental Hotel - 2nd level Services: Lunch | Dinner', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/b7/69/52/we-highly-recommend-our.jpg', 'Birdcage', '5', 'http://www.intercontinental.com/cai-semiramis', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(63, 'First Floor, JW Marriott Hotel Ring Road, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Indulge in flavorsome delicacies from Hong Kong, Thailand, Singapore and the mainland of China. Enjoy skillfully and authentically prepared dim sum, soups, main dishes and salads. Also enjoy one of the refreshing Lemongrass signature juice blends.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/13/5c/43/8f/indulge-in-mouthwatering.jpg', 'Lemongrass', '5', 'http://www.jwmarriottcairolife.com/restaurant/hotels/hotel-information/travel/caijw/dining/lemongrass', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(64, 'Katameya Heights New Cairo - 5th District, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'The Smokery is a chain of upscale restaurants located in the most stunning and prestigious locations in Egypt: Katameya Heights, Heliopolis, Palm Hills, El Gouna, and the North Coast. The Smokery provides a unique experience with its diverse menu in its charming and exclusive settings producing some of the finest smoked salmon in the World.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/21/8f/12/4f/your-perfect-outdoor.jpg', 'The Smokery', '4.5', 'http://www.thesmokeryrestaurants.com/home', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(65, 'Triumph Luxury Hotel Block 19 In Front Of Katameya Heights, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', '? El-Khan ? is an oriental restaurant where you can enjoy a truly authentic unforgettable dining experience, flavors from around the Middle East are brought together, we are looking forward to have you to make sure you leave with a happy tummy.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1f/96/90/58/caption.jpg', 'El-khan Restaurant', '5', 'http://triumphhotel.com/luxury-home/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(66, 'Galae Square Galae Square, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Giannini\'s is a story that is inspired by the unique style of cooking developed by the Italians who migrated to New York. It is based on the precious recipes carried by Italians to their new homes in New York; dishes to remind the family of home and to keep their values and traditions together. Giannini?s is with a Nile view that makes it a good choice for any gathering, meeting or romantic dinner. There is a private part at Giannini?s that can be reserved for business lunch, meetings', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/12/9c/92/f1/photo3jpg.jpg', 'Giannini?s New York Italian Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/gianninisrestaurant/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(67, 'Royal Maxim Palace Kempinski Cairo, First Settlement, New Cairo First Settlement, New Cairo, Cairo 00000 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Grab your chopsticks and dig into the best of Asian cuisine in Cairo as you savour the bursting flavours of Yana?s signature dishes, prepared with homemade spice blends, flavourful sauces and the passion of our chef. Whether you are planning a fine business dinner or an intimate gathering, enjoy the contemporary setting of our semi-private dining room, which can accommodate up to ten guests.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/3c/12/12/yana-thai-restaurant.jpg', 'Yana', '5', 'http://www.kempinski.com/en/cairo/royal-maxim-palace-kempinski-cairo/dining/restaurants/yana/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(68, '13 El Thawra St El Korba, Heliopolis, Cairo 11757 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Inspired by the Heliopolis of the mid 1900s; a place to make time for making time. Charlie\'s is a nod to the godfather of Egyptian hospitality, Charles Baehler. In the mid 1900s, Cairo was buzzing with a unique melange of Egyptian and European cultural influences, much like the spirit of Heliopolis itself. Charles was a connector of experiences. And today, we celebrate the culture of leisure he brought and say: chapeau monsieur!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1b/a0/9e/1a/charlie-s-restaurant.jpg', 'Charlie\'s Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Charlies-Restaurant-107499210777229/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(69, 'Hilton Cairo Heliopolis Uruba Street Heliopolis, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Lan Tania; an authentic Thai cuisine restaurant serving a wide variety of seafood, beef, chicken, vegetarian options, and Pad Thai, all within an entertaining show kitchen. Open from 2:00 PM to midnight. Closed on Saturdays. Enjoy the Taste of Thai Cuisine with your families and friends. Family Friendly', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/67/fb/5f/lan-tania.jpg', 'Lan Tania', '5', 'http://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/caihehi-hilton-cairo-heliopolis/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(70, '136 Nile Street, Cairo 12311 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Savour the finest cuts of meat at our steakhouse, also serving cocktails shaken to perfection, aboard the First Nile Boat.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/3a/d3/b1/xodo-interior.jpg', 'Xodo', '5', 'https://www.fourseasons.com/cairofr/dining/restaurants/xodo/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(71, '1189 Nile Corniche 1189 Nile Corniche, Cairo 11221 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'La Zisa is a modern and relaxed dining space that offers authentic Southern Italian cuisine where guests can enjoy their dining experience overlooking bright views of the Nile.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/b7/68/7d/la-zisa.jpg', 'La Zisa', '5', 'http://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/caixr-the-st-regis-cairo/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(72, '22 El-farik Abd El-moniem Riad Dokki, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'A casual diner offering customers a selection of international dishes and items to share, satisfying their everyday food cravings.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/25/80/9b/9a/meaet.jpg', 'Meaet', '5', 'http://www.Facebook.com/meaetegypt', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(73, '5A By The Waterway, New Cairo 3, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'A family-style restaurant franchised from Dubai that combines the highest level of service (delivered personally by the chefs themselves); meticulously chosen, quality ingredients and signature mocktails all served in a serenely designed and welcoming interior.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/29/88/8c/77/a-name-and-flavour-that.jpg', 'Reif Kushiyaki Cairo', '5', 'http://www.reifkushiyakiegypt.com', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(74, '90th Street Concord Plaza Mall, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'The Famous Turkish Brand opened its 394th branch Worldwide & the first in Cairo, Egypt. All this in the valuable experience IN MADO CAIRO', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/25/0a/b0/26/authentic-turkish-food.jpg', 'Mado', '5', 'http://www.mado.menu', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(75, '17 Al Bostan St, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Inspired by the Japanese word meaning ?CHILD OF JOY? Sachi is where stories are told, and happy experiences are recalled. Our passion drives every detail of your dishes at Sachi Park St. All of our plates have their own individual story. It might be about where the ingredients come from, or maybe a particular flavor evokes the memory of a cherished holiday. And we love to share these stories with our guests. With Sachi?s dishes, you?re not just enjoying a plate ? though, of course, we hope you are anyway! You?re also being invited to step inside the modern Asian-Mediterranean Era.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/22/d5/b5/3a/sachi-park-st-logo.jpg', 'Sachi Park St', '5', 'http://www.sachirestaurant.com/park-st', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(76, 'Nile City Towers- 2005 B Corniche El Nil, Cairo 11311 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Fairmont Nile City\'s latest Italian concept brings authentic Italian cuisine to the capital. The all-day dining restaurant starts its day with a lavish breakfast buffet before transforming into a stylish lunch and dinner spot. For a hip night out, enjoy cocktails and music at the trendy bar. The restaurant draws its inspiration from warm, coastal countries to ensure the perfect ambiance. The natural elements and cozy leather lounges add the right amount of luxurious comfort. Inspired by Mediterranean colors and shades, the restaurant draws its inspiration from warm, coastal countries. To create the perfect ambiance, natural wooden elements and cozy leather lounges add the right amount of luxurious comfort.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/23/71/8f/italian-restaurant.jpg', 'L\'Uliveto Italian Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.fairmont.com/nile-city-cairo/dining/l-uliveto/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(77, 'Hilton Cairo Heliopolis El Orouba Street, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Egyptian Night; a genuine Egyptian Restaurant, featuring barbecue fare and live entertainment. Family-friendly.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/67/db/0b/egyptian-nights-restaurant.jpg', 'Egyptian Night', '5', 'http://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/caihehi-hilton-cairo-heliopolis/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(78, 'Ring Road, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'JW Steakhouse Restaurant Mirage City has reopened its doors after a remarkable renovation, where you can enjoy the city?s best Contemporary American grill specialties masterfully crafted by our culinary team. Open for dinner Reservations required l Minimum Age: 16 years old accompanied by parents l Dress code: Smart Elegant (No Jeans)', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/21/ef/50/b1/bourbon-bar.jpg', 'JW Steakhouse Cairo Mirage City', '5', 'https://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/caijw-jw-marriott-hotel-cairo/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(79, 'Royal Maxim Palace Kempinski Hotel, First Settlement, New Cairo First Settlement, New Cairo, Cairo 11477 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'The finest of oriental cuisines in Cairo infused with Egyptian and Levant flavours and a subtle combination of spices. Bab Al Qasr sets the stage for an authentic dinner in ambient surroundings, accented with belly dance performances on selected nights. With a setting that reflects Arabian hospitality, Bab Al Qasr invites your family and friends to gather around the table and sample a variety of your favourites of all time from the Middle Eastern cuisine in addition to a wide selection of shisha flavours.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1d/a8/a6/9e/1-metre-kofta-at-bab.jpg', 'Bab Al Qasr', '5', 'http://www.kempinski.com/en/cairo/royal-maxim-palace-kempinski-cairo/dining/restaurants/bab-al-qasr/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(80, 'InterContinental Cairo Semiramis Corniche El Nile Downtown, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'The Grill presents the unique flavors of contemporary, traditional & brasserie French and fine dining cuisine for dinner in an elegant ambiance overlooking the Nile. Open daily from 7 pm for dinner. Located on the third floor at the Semiramis InterContinental', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/29/c3/e4/31/the-grill-presents-the.jpg', 'The Grill Restaurant & Lounge', '5', 'http://www.intercontinental.com/cai-semiramis', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(81, 'Corniche El Nile Semiramis Intercontinental Hotel, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Only the finest ingredients have been hand-selected for an authentic taste of Italy at Pane Vino. Share the universal passion for pasta and pizza alongside a glass of wine from our extensive wine cellar and enjoy panoramic Nile views indoors and outdoors at the Pane Vino restaurant & terrace. Open daily for lunch and dinner. Located on the second floor at the Semiramis InterContinental Cairo.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/91/08/29/enjoy-an-upbeat-taste.jpg', 'Pane Vino Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.ihg.com/intercontinental/hotels/gb/en/cairo/croha/hoteldetail#scmisc=nav_hoteldetail_undefined', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(82, '1 Latin America Street Garden City, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Excusite Lebanese Food in Oriental Setting. Truly a Feast for the Eyes and the Taste buds!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/05/67/2d/b0/taboula.jpg', 'Taboula Lebanese Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/#!/TaboulaEgypt', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51');
