(83, '1189 Nile Corniche The St. Regis Hotel, Cairo 11221 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'At Tianma, you are taken on a journey to Singapore; the Lion City, experiencing the South-East Asian culture; as its menu items feature a contemporary mixture of Singapore\'s best cuisines: Chinese, Indian, and Southeast Asian.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/4a/cb/e2/tianma-our-authentic.jpg', 'Tianma', '5', 'https://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/caixr-the-st-regis-cairo/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(84, 'Corniche El Nil Semiramis InterContinental Cairo, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Sabaya may be rooted in Lebanese tradition, but Chef Walid Bazl is willing to branch out with contemporary flair. Mezzas are the magic of the menu, with hot and cold options including Kebbe Nayye, Stuffed Vine Leaves, Hommow Bil Awarma, Makanik and Cheese Manaqish. In accordance with Lebanese custom, you?ll be brought to the lounge for after-dinner tea, sweets and conversation.Location: In the Semiramis InterContinental Cairo Hotel - 2nd level Services: Lunch | Dinner', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/ee/2b/ce/sabaya-is-one-of-cairo.jpg', 'Sabaya', '4.5', 'http://www.ihg.com/intercontinental/hotels/us/en/cairo/croha/hoteldetail', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(85, '159 26th of July Street Zamalek, Cairo 11211 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Delicious creations and authentic recipes, perfected. Life is beautiful, taste it here!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0d/c6/9b/72/warm-and-cozy-delicious.jpg', 'O\'s Pasta', '4.5', 'http://www.ospasta.com', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(86, 'Katameya Dunes, Road 90 The Westin Cairo Golf Resort & Spa, Cairo 11835 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Mar‚ Social is an intimate taberna-style restaurant & bar inspired by the Two Starred Michelin Chef Henrique Sa Pessoa. This restaurant & petiscos bar is a Mediterranean, Spanish and Portuguese traditional cuisine with a modern twist that fits the upscale casual dining crowd.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/28/fd/cc/ab/mare-social-facade.jpg', 'Mare Social', '5', 'https://www.maresocialrestaurant.com/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(87, 'Royal Maxim Palace Kempinski Cairo, First Settlement, New Cairo First Settlement, New Cairo, Cairo 11477 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Lucca adapts the flavours of Italian classics into a range of home-style recipes, cooked with the best ingredients of the Mediterranean combined with the passion of our Italian chef to present you with the essence of the Italian cuisine in Cairo. Experience the enchanting Italian ambience with a touch of art at Royal Maxim Palace Kempinski, where Italian scenic wall paintings offer you a laid-back casual daylight lunch by the pool or an intimate romantic dinner.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/28/48/7e/9f/lucca-is-the-place-where.jpg', 'Lucca', '4.5', 'http://www.kempinski.com/en/cairo/royal-maxim-palace-kempinski-cairo/dining/restaurants/lucca/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(88, '1113 Corniche El Nil St The Nile Ritz Carlton, Cairo 11221 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Overlooking the Nile, Bar?Oro brings the elegance of a classic cocktail bar to downtown Cairo. Signature cocktails are paired with Italian-inspired apertivos, or small bites, and a walk-humidor houses an impressive selection of Cuban cigars.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/16/d9/34/5d/bar-oro-means-the-golden.jpg', 'Bar\'Oro', '5', 'http://www.ritzcarlton.com/en/hotels/middle-east/cairo/dining/bar-oro', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(89, '4 Al Badeya Street Heliopolis, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'ESC? is an upscale contemporary dining restaurant which is located in the heart of Heliopolis. ESC? strives for the renaissance of contemporary dining, inspired by the Latin art and culture, transformed into mediterranean taste. The word ESC? is derived from the old Latin origin which means ?Delicious Bites, Flavourful Food.?', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/12/29/8c/a3/exquisite-vine-cellar.jpg', 'ESCA', '5', 'http://www.escahospitality.com/esca-heliopolis', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(90, 'Royal Maxim Palace Kempinski Hotel First Settlement, New Cairo, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'ROMANOV EUROPEAN GRILL ROOM Romanov invites you to experience our European Grill Room at its finest with a range of premium meat cuts and seafood selections prepared with bursting flavours on and off the grill. Taking its name from the great family of Russian rulers, the elegant design of this European grill room enthrals diners in a serene dinner encounter with candle lit table set-ups overlooking the majestic courtyard of Royal Maxim Palace Kempinski.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1d/a8/b4/6d/the-view-at-romanov.jpg', 'Romanov', '5', 'http://www.kempinski.com/en/cairo/royal-maxim-palace-kempinski-cairo/dining/restaurants/romanov', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(91, '16 Saray El Gezirah St Zamalek, Cairo 11211 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Dine in an ultimate American Bistro experience . Feast on your favorite burger; in a fund filled hip atmosphere. Located ground floor of Zamalek tower . Open daily from 12 noon - 12 mid night located on ground floor of Zamalek tower . open daily from 12 noon to 12 midnight\"', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/21/88/88/b0/roy-s-smokehouse-restaurant.jpg', 'Roy\'s Smokehouse', '4.5', 'http://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/caieg-cairo-marriott-hotel-and-omar-khayyam-casino/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(92, 'Saray El Gezirah Street Zamalek, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'This classic French Restaurant with train-like booths, ?Gar‡ons? in traditional French style aprons and vests and an art nouveau feel will transport you into Parisian bistros of the Belle poque. Excellent French Gastronomic cuisine, an extensive wine list and a water level Nile view combine to make Le Steak one of Cairo?s favorite dining experiences.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/27/37/e5/a0/just-a-lovely-friday.jpg', 'Le Steak Restaurant - Le Pacha 1901', '4.5', 'http://www.lepacha.com', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(93, 'InterContinental Cairo Semiramis Hotel Corniche El Nil, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Sushiramis uses only the freshest ingredients coupled with meticulous preparation to create a range of mouth-watering Sushi and delectable Sashimi. Savour our Sushiramis Maki prepared with grilled eggplant, molasses and smoked eel, now available at Sushiramis restaurant and in all our restaurants. Located on the lobby level a the Semiramis InterContinental Cairo.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/83/a9/cb/sushiramis-speaks-for.jpg', 'Sushiramis', '5', 'http://www.ihg.com/intercontinental/hotels/us/en/cairo/croha/hoteldetail', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(94, 'InterContinental Cairo Citystars Omar Ibn El Khattab St. Heliopolis, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Home style Italian cooking is given a gourmet twist at this popular restaurant where traditional recipes take on a refined new flavour.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/94/ba/3f/maestro-italian-restaurant.jpg', 'Maestro Italian Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.intercontinental.com/icheliopolis', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(95, '16 Saray El Gezira Street Cairo Marriott Hotel, Cairo 11211 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Indulge your desire for a great steak at JW Steakhouse with your favorite cut of USDA prime beef cooked to order. Our steak house restaurant also serves farm fresh sides and dessert offerings that are the perfect ending to a great meal Reservations required', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/21/e1/c1/2f/jw-s-steakhouse-restaurant.jpg', 'JW Steakhouse Restaurant', '4.5', 'https://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/caieg-cairo-marriott-hotel-and-omar-khayyam-casino/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(96, '136 Nile Street, Cairo 12311 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Gaze out at panoramic Nile views while you explore the best of pan-Asian cuisine ? Chinese, Indian, Japanese and Thai ? at our contemporary restaurant and lounge by the Nile aboard the First Nile Boat.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/3b/0a/c8/interior-of-nairu-restaurant.jpg', 'Nairu Restaurant and Lounge', '5', 'https://www.fourseasons.com/cairofr/dining/restaurants/nairu-and-nairu-lounge/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(97, '3 Cleopatra Street Cairo, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Ayadina is a fine dining Lebanese Eatery, inspired from the phrase ?with our own hands? to ensure the sense of home-welcoming. We strive to bring you authentic Lebanese flavors, delightful atmosphere, and a welcoming team. With our elegant ambiance and inventive Lebanese menu you are guaranteed to revel in a gratifying and cozy experience all together.available at the following locations: City Stars Mall - Point 90 Mall - Korba - Mall of Arabia - Alexandria Tivoli Boulevard', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/75/42/9c/clean-and-nicely-decorated.jpg', 'Ayadina - Korba', '4.5', 'http://www.ayadina.restaurant/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(98, 'Omar Ibn El Khattab, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'This casual outdoor bar is the perfect place to unwind with a refreshing cocktail or a fresh juice. You can also enjoy a tempting variety of sandwiches, snacks and shisha by the swimming pool.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/29/63/e4/7d/dishes.jpg', 'Pool Bar', '5', 'http://www.ihg.com/intercontinental/hotels/gb/en/cairo/crohc/hoteldetail/about-the-hotel/dining', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(99, 'El khalig street, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'A unique blend of modern and ancient Asian decor with low Japanese tables and an extensive Sushi Bar. The delicious cuisine features an exotic selection of specialties from China, Japan, Thailand and India. In recognition of its outstanding food and service, L?Asiatique was voted third best restaurant in Africa, top best in Egypt, by the World?s 50 Best Restaurants', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/96/c1/13/l-asiatique-le-pacha.jpg', 'L\'Asiatique - Le Pacha 1901', '4.5', 'http://www.lepacha.com/restaurants/lasiatique/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(100, '66 Omar Ibn El Khattab St, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Rossini Restaurant was established in 1993 in Cairo and Florence offering a wide range of exquisite Italian and Seafood specialties. The setting is a Mediterranean style villa in the heart of Heliopolis. We succeeded over the years to build a solid reputation and a wide network of loyal guests whom we consider Egypt\'s elite.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/27/00/49/90/make-rossini-your-weekend.jpg', 'Rossini Restaurant', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/rossinirestaurantegypt/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(101, 'Fairmont Nile City Nile City Towers - 2005B, Corniche El Nil, Ramlet Beaulac, Cairo 2466 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Experience Bab El Nil?s oriental dishes and local entertainment featuring some of the city\'s finest entertainers and belly dancers. Bab El Nil is set to provide you with both an indoor and an outdoor experience full of vivid colors, arabesque designs and a unique living wall as you enjoy an authentically local setting overlooking stunning views of the river Nile. As for football and TV fans, enjoy watching all the big leagues and your favorite channels on Bab El Nil?s 138-inch HD screen alongside an extensive selection of the best shisha flavors in town.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/12/20/58/7b/bab-el-nil-restaurant.jpg', 'Bab El Nil Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.fairmont.com/nile-city-cairo/dining/bab-el-nil/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(102, '1189 Nile Corniche St. Regis Cairo, Cairo 11221 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Poolside restaurant and bar at The St. Regis Cairo Hotel, offering a relaxing escape from the city with stunning views of the Nile.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/25/7f/e0/42/enjoy-refreshing-salads.jpg', 'Sirocco', '5', 'http://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/caixr-the-st-regis-cairo/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(103, 'El Saheed Sayed Zakaria Street Heliopolis Towers, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Pizza Bar: Pizza Bar offers a contemporary outdoor dining experience. Enjoy a light meal at our modern terrace overlooking the gardens and the swimming pool area. Our team would be delighted to prepare a broad range of refreshing cocktails and mocktails while enjoying a perfect Shisha set up at an authentic Shisha corner by the pool. Broadcasting life matches and sports. Dress code: Smart - Casual Family Friendly', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/77/ca/59/pizza-bar.jpg', 'Pizza Bar', '5', 'http://waldorfastoria3.hilton.com/en/hotels/egypt/heliopolis-towers-hotel-CAIWEWA/amenities/restaurants.html', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(104, '3 El Thawra Council Street, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Journey deep into Moroccan culture inLa Palmaraie, with traditional live music, belly-dancing and the sociable traditions of mint tea and flavored shisha. Settle down under the arches of a monumental patio where wood and golden light contrast with the blue of the night and the reflections of the Nile. For an intimate experience surrounded by lush foliage, reserve an exclusive terrace overlooking the river Nile. Decorated with watercolors by Egyptian artist Aleyaa Kamal, the menu represents a travel journal. Flip through it and be tempted by a wide selection of tagines, briouat pastries, savory pastilla pies and couscous.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/24/f2/5a/d8/la-palmeraie-restaurant.jpg', 'La Palmeraie', '4.5', 'http://www.sofitel-cairo-nile-elgezirah.com/restaurants-bars/la-palmeraie-restaurant/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(105, '1089 Corniche El Nil Four Seasons Hotel Cairo at Nile Plaza, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Indulge in Egyptian fattah, mezzah or maa\'moul with keshta whenever you like at Zitouni, our 24-hour restaurant serving authentic Egyptian fare overlooking the Nile. With interior d‚cor inspired by Fatimid Cairo and large windows overlooking an endless panoramic view of the Nile, everything about Zitouni gives Egyptian dining the grandeur it deserves. An extensive buffet display situated near the open kitchen offers breakfast, lunch and dinner in addition to an impressive all-day ?Friday Brunch? buffet. A team of talented Egyptian chefs led by Chef Moataz Said oversee the kitchen to ensure true authenticity in the preparation of the wide range of mezzeh, Egyptian bread and grilled dishes.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/19/37/4a/5e/zitouni-egyptian-restaurant.jpg', 'Zitouni', '4.5', 'http://www.fourseasons.com/caironp/dining/restaurants/zitouni/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(106, '1089 Corniche El Nil Garden City, Cairo 11519 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Feeling lucky? At 8 ? named after Chinese culture\'s luckiest number ? explore a wide range of traditional Cantonese dishes and delicacies. From heavenly Dim Sum Friday Brunch, flawless dinner experiences to Chef Chen?s home-made noodles, all make dining at 8 restaurant a truly exceptional experience. 8 welcomes you with two private dining rooms that can accommodate up to 20 guests for your intimate gatherings, along with another private seating area that is perfect for celebratory dinners and can accommodate from 2 to 6 guests.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/19/37/0d/3e/8-chinese-restaurant.jpg', '8 Chinese Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.fourseasons.com/caironp/dining/restaurants/8/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(107, '16 Saray El Gezira Street. Zamalek Cairo Marriott Hotel & Omar Khayyam Casino, Cairo 11211 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Specialty: Afternoon Tea from 2:00 p.m. till 6:00 p.m. * Entertainment: Daily from 7:30 p.m. till 10:30 p.m * Admission: Age 12 years-old & above.Open from 11:00 am till 01:00 am.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/08/b1/8f/5b/saraya-gallery.jpg', 'Saraya Gallery', '4.5', 'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/caieg-cairo-marriott-hotel-and-omar-khayyam-casino/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(108, 'Heliopolis Towers Uruba Street, Heliopolis, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Aqua e Luce offers casual dining with an essence of striking modern interiors. With glowing lights under glass floors, rich leather seats and a warm environment featuring water streams and palm trees creating the perfect backdrop for delicious menu choices including salads, steaks and fish all prepared by our talented Chefs. Enjoy delicious brunch with kid?s entertainment every Friday. Aqua e Luce?s spectacular ?Show? kitchen and tropical Atrium lobby view is perfect for relaxing and enjoying a tasty meal. All Day Dinning-Dress code: Smart - Casual', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/82/91/e5/aqua-e-luce.jpg', 'Aqua e Luce', '5', 'http://waldorfastoria3.hilton.com/en/hotels/egypt/heliopolis-towers-hotel-CAIWEWA/amenities/restaurants.html', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(109, 'El Saheed Sayed Zakaria Street El- Orouba street, Cairo 24666 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Sink into a cozy sofa and enjoy live music at this warm and inviting lobby bar, serving perfectly prepared cocktails, Mocktails, wine and champagne as well as a selection of light bar fare. Open 24 Hours.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/17/9c/65/9f/tell-travellers-more.jpg', 'Fuze Bar', '5', 'http://waldorfastoria3.hilton.com/en/hotels/egypt/heliopolis-towers-hotel-CAIWEWA/index.html', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(110, 'Ring Road Renaissance Cairo Mirage City Hotel, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Step into a uniquely designed bar, with floor to ceiling windows with panoramic views of Mirage City. Spend time and discover our wide array of premium brand drinks or dinner.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/29/68/ef/83/vintage-bar-lounge.jpg', 'Vintage Bar & Lounge', '4.5', 'http://www.morecravings.com/en/venues/vintage-bar-lounge', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(111, '275 Mokarrar St. New Maadi, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Africa\'s 1st and ONLY AVPN-certified pizzeria (member number 851 & 932). We use time-tested techniques, high quality ingredients, and an AVPN-approved handmade Neapolitan brick oven to bring a little piece of Naples to Cairo.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/27/b4/4b/b0/pizza.jpg', 'What The Crust - Maadi', '5', 'http://www.whatthecrust.com', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(112, '26th of July St, Zamalek, Gezira Island Intersection of 26th of July and Shagaret El Dor,, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Here at Zooba, we turn familiar Egyptian street food on its head (and dress it up a little, too). We use only the freshest local produce to create simple, flavorful, gourmet dishes.We don\'t just use locally-sourced products in our food; we also reclaim local materials and found objects to create an eclectic dining space that pays homage to the creative resourcefulness and colorful spirit of the Egyptian people.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/03/44/c2/b2/zooba.jpg', 'Zooba', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/ZoobaEats', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(113, 'Hilton Cairo Heliopolis El Orouba Street, Heliopolis, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Maria?s:Serving authentic Mexican cuisine from the recognized Salsa and Chips to ?Carne Asada? (Charcoal Grilled Dry Beef), homemade corn tortillas and delicious Guacamole prepared table side. Enjoy our favorite appetizers and our wide selection of Mexican cocktails. Our Chef and team are looking forward to dazzle you with their amazing Ceviches. Open from 04:00PM till Midnight- Dress code: Smart - Casual. Family Friendly', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/68/0c/c5/maria-s.jpg', 'MARIA\'S', '5', 'http://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/caihehi-hilton-cairo-heliopolis/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(114, '16 Saray El Gezira Street Marriott Hotel, Cairo 11211 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Heavenly antipasti, soups and mains from Italy to your table. Ground Floor of the Palace. Restaurant located on the ground floor of the palace .Open from 6pm ? 12am.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/14/51/f4/e4/ristorante-tuscany-offers.jpg', 'Ristorante Tuscany', '4.5', 'http://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/caieg-cairo-marriott-hotel-and-omar-khayyam-casino/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(115, 'Corniche El Nil, Semiramis InterContinental Cairo, Cairo 11511 Egypt Garden City, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'India along the Nile takes you on an unmatched gastronomical journey through the valleys of India, bringing you an array of dishes from its diverse regions, served in a contemporary and modern atmosphere. Our signature resto-bar offers an array of delectable a la carte dishes infused with Indian flavours and flair, including a ?tasting menu? designed for sharing and ideal for sampling. For a more private?and captivating?experience, India along the Nile offers semi-private dining areas, perfect for intimate gatherings.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/15/75/4d/d3/masala-prawn-biryani.jpg', 'India along the Nile', '4.5', 'http://www.intercontinental.com/hotels/gb/en/cairo/croha/hoteldetail?qAdlt=1&qBrs=6c.hi.ex.rs.ic.cp.in.sb.cw.cv.ul.vn.ki.sp.nd.ct&qChld=0&qFRA=1&qGRM=0&qIta=99612192&qPSt=0&qRRSrt=rt&qRef=df&qRms=1&qRpn=1&qRpp=20&qSHp=1&qSmP=3&qSrt=sBR&qWch=0&srb_u=1&icdv=99612192&dp=true&glat=SEAR', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(116, '1115 Corniche El Nile Ramses Hilton, Cairo 12344 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Your gateway to delicious and healthy Mediterranean cuisine, offering a wide range of dishes inspired by coastal towns. Indulge in delicious seafood dishes, and a variety of other options, all prepared using the finest local ingredients and imported Mediterranean treasures.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/0b/f3/11/23/delecious-fresh-lobster.jpg', 'Citadel Grill', '4.5', 'https://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/cairhtw-ramses-hilton/dining/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(117, '114 El-Moez Street, El-Gamaleya In Front of Al Suheimi House, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Dotted with picturesque minarets, domes, and medieval architecture, the surrounding scenery from the rooftop takes you back to a mystical, alluring time in Egyptian history. Enjoy the surroundings of the Fatimid town whilst tasting home cooking at our authentic rooftop restaurant.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/27/ea/23/5d/zeeyara-terrace.jpg', 'Zeeyara Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.instagram.com/zeeyara.restaurant/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(118, '15 Hoda Shaarawy Street Downtown, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Founded by A. Zaghloul in 1959, in the heart of the greater Cairo, Felfela has become one of the most iconic restaurants in Egypt. Felfela is the first restaurant to promote the Egyptian and the Mediterranean cuisine inside and outside of Egypt. With its very authentic decoration, Felfela offers a unique experience and not just a place to eat. Only in our restaurant, you can feel the originality of the typical oriental decoration that symbolizes the traditions of the Egyptian society. Perfection and excellence are our trademark. Do not miss the opportunity to live this unique experience ! Felfela Downtown is operating under a different management than other branches.?', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/14/bc/89/d4/foul-and-falafel.jpg', 'Felfela', '4', 'http://www.felfelaegypt.com', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(119, '1191 Corniche El Nil, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Discover the delicious flavors of the modern Lebanese cuisine at the renowned restaurant Oak Grill with a unique Mediterranean touch. Experience our signature dishes expertly prepared by our professional chef including Fattouch with grilled halloumi, Bourgoul with Oak smoked chicken, Osmaliyeh Halloumi sticks, Oak smoked Sea Bass Shawarma, Duo of Oak smoked duck and chicken accompanied by soothing piano tunes from our resident pianist at dinner A fashionable d‚cor, chic mood lighting and candle-lit tables create the ideal venue for a romantic meal or special dinner.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/88/a4/6f/oak-grill-by-joe-barza.jpg', 'Oak Grill', '4.5', 'http://conradhotels3.hilton.com/en/hotels/egypt/conrad-cairo-CAICICI/amenities/restaurants-oak-grill.html', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(120, 'Corniche El NIl InterContinental Semiramis Cairo, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Nile Terrace offers outdoor pleasures under a starlit sky. With the Nile as a backdrop, the scene is set for the ultimate \"en plein air\" experience, delicious BBQ, whilst enjoying live entertainment and games on a giant screen. Open daily for dinner, Located on the 4th floor at the Semiramis InterContinental Cairo.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/04/36/5d/nile-terrace-where-tempting.jpg', 'Nile Terrace', '4.5', 'http://www.ihg.com/intercontinental/hotels/gb/en/cairo/croha', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(121, '9 Palestine Street, Inside Bandar Mall New Maadi, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', '\"Fuego\", Grill and Sushi bar, is an upscale casual restaurant, Since 2008 In Cairo; It presents a new concept to Egypt that combines a joyful dining experience and a unique ambiance with an innovative interior design decoration. The menu is derived from the popular Californian cuisine that offers the best quality food in addition to a wide selection of the finest Australian steaks, chops , seafood, pasta, soups, starters and desserts. It?s worth to mention the luxurious cozy experience that feeds off the energy coming out of the open kitchen where you can watch your food, being cooked for you if you do choose so. Since Sushi has become part of the Cali-Culture and no longer just a Japanese cuisine, Fuego encompasses the healthiest authentic Japanese Sushi ever. There is an exquisite Sushi bar that centers the dining room. You can directly talk to our sushi chefs and watch them prepare your order while enjoying a lavish and cozy environment at the barstool. Fuego is an unforgettable dining experience that offers: ambiance, quality of food, service and hospitality which are clearly displayed through our well distinguished chefs and our handpicked service team. We are looking forward to serving you.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0a/08/26/44/fuego-grill-and-sushi.jpg', 'Fuego Grill And Sushi Bar', '4', 'http://www.fuego.com.eg/', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(122, '49 El Nozha Street Heliopolis, Cairo 11511 Egypt', 'Cairo', 'Blaze Resto is the ultimate get together for friends to escape the hustle and bustle of their busy days. Merging international dishes from American, Italian and Tex-Mex cuisines, and deliciously prepared by our internationally renowned chefs from fresh ingredients. It all comes together with a cozy and contemporary setting along a welcoming staff that brings you back for more. we are located at the following addresses: City Stars Mall ? Mohandessin - Mall of Arabia - Alexandria Tivoli Boulevard', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/18/46/48/12/mall-of-arabia-branch.jpg', 'Blaze Restaurant & Cafe', '4.5', 'http://www.blazeegypt.com', 13, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(123, 'Mashraba close to Penguin Village, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Our day off is on monday', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/04/75/3d/23/lakhbatita-ramez-paola.jpg', 'Ramez & Paola Restaurant', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/ramezpaolalakhbatita', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(124, 'El Masbat St, Dahab 8772513 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Good for: Child-friendly, Romantic, Groups, Business, Local cuisine Excellent, Entertaining clients, Cheap EatsDining options Brunch, lunch, dinner, booking, until last night', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/02/6b/18/8e/filename-dsc-2301-jpg.jpg', 'El Fanar', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/elfanardahab/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(125, 'El Melal Street Eel Garden, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Food Urge is open for breakfast from 9 am until 9 pm for dinner. We offer freshly prepared and cooked meals, snacks and drinks using locally produced fare. Our food is clean and tasty and we have one of the best views in Dahab, on the beach to enjoy. We do not use plastic and we are aiming to be 100% single-use plastic free within our restaurant as part of our conservation and recycling efforts. We have managed to eradicate the use of plastic water bottles, saving up to 10,000 plastic bottles a year. We also do not sell fish here to minimize the impact of local fishing.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/02/2a/bb/b6/welcome-to-food-urge.jpg', 'Food Urge', '5', 'http://dive-urge.com/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(126, 'Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Egyptian cuisine, presents homemade food with fresh ingredients, warm hospitality and served with lovely smile.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/16/ec/3a/3c/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Si Omar Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/Si-Omar-restaurant-428860147635540/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(127, '3 El Melil Street Light House Area, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Cozy, welcoming, beautiful coffee shop and restaurant, that roasts its own coffee beans and makes the best coffees ever, serves delicious milkshakes, bakes its pizzas in an Italian stove oven, offers generous servings of pasta dishes, and serves a super tasty homemade banana cake and tantalizing chocolate-banana pancakes - all this in a gorgeous backyard garden-terrace intimate atmosphere where you will really feel at home. (Take away and delivery also available).', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/06/06/b2/55/athanor-coffee-shop-and.jpg', 'Athanor Cafe-Pizzeria', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Athanor-Cafe-Pizzeria-891097314287382/?ref=page_internal', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(128, 'El Madaris Street Shams Hotel & Dive Centre, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Shams Restaurant is located right on the beach and offers wonderful views of the Gulf of Aqaba and of the sunset each and every day. Our restaurant offers a large choice of International and Egyptian cuisine, with the Egyptian cuisine being a combination of Turkish, Arabic and Mediterranean ethnic and fusion dishes, and including various vegetarian options.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/0d/56/f5/d8/bedouin-style-sitting.jpg', 'Shams Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://shamsdahab.com/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(129, 'Beside Entrance of Tarakhan Hotel The Mamsha Promenade by the Sea, Lighthouse Area, Opposite Sababa Hotel, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'At Caf‚ Paris, we unveil to you many of France\'s culinary secrets dating back as far as the Middle ages; from the simple crunchy baguette to the rich sauces, creamy gratins, and luscious pastries, French cuisine has undeniably inspired and shaped Western gastronomy into what it is today. So hold on to your baguettes, get your cheese platter ready, as we dive into what makes Caf‚ Paris your delicious French gourmet experience... Bon appetit!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/21/98/16/77/caption.jpg', 'Cafe Paris', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/cafeparisdahab', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(130, 'Lighthouse In The Entrance Of Lighthouse Diving Site, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Hell\'s Kitchen offers a casual dining experience in a relaxed, friendly atmosphere. A glance at the menu reveals a wide variety of dishes from around the world, using the freshest, seasonal products on the market, cooked with professional love and care. Vegan, vegetarian and gluten-free diners are also catered for.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/1d/81/00/0a/lvcx.jpg', 'Hell\'s Kitchen Dahab', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/Hells-Kitchen-Dahab-by-Gordon-Ramses-970602563012606/?fref=ts', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(131, 'Masbath, Dahab, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Friends restaurant in Dahab is one of the most famous places with chilly atmosphere and nice food', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/2e/d6/37/photo0jpg.jpg', 'Friends', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/friends.restaurant.1988/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(132, 'Beachside Promenade Masbat Bay, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Shark Restaurant Dahab. Cooking with Love. Serving with a Smile!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/02/78/0b/79/filename-the-feast-jpg.jpg', 'Shark Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://sharkrestaurantdahab.weebly.com/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(133, 'H20 Dive Centre, 2nd Floor., Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'We are a team of three partners, all cookers, we do the best quality we can we the most affordable prices to feed all. We are very creative and generous with our dishes. Most of our dishes entirely tastez home made.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/26/75/8e/da/american-platter-dish.jpg', 'Tim\'s Munch', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Timsmunch/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(134, 'Light House Area Masbat, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Yalla Bar & Restaurant is the place to be in Dahab! Meet people, enjoy the delicious food and drink with great hospitality and atmosphere!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/92/9d/11/yalla-bar-restaurant.jpg', 'Yalla Bar & Restaurant', '4', 'http://www.yallabar.com', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(135, 'El Melal Street Eel Garden, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'A friendly, welcoming family owned business located in one of the best spots Dahab can offer, right on the sea front at Eel Garden Dive and Snorkelling site. We offer you tasty, freshly prepared food all day long, from light snacks to full evening meals prepared to order; including Egyptian Cuisine. If it?s not on the menu, ask us for your favourite dish and we will do our best to rustle something special up for you. If you?re just looking for a place to sip a few cold drinks and spend the day chilling we also offer a variety of refreshing hot and cold drinks, freshly squeezed fruit juices and tasty Smoothies. Enjoy our comfortable, Egyptian/Bedouin style low seated dining area, dedicated sun lounging section with plenty of beds to laze on and soak up some rays, and a little chill out zone on our roof terrace offering the most amazing panoramic views as far as the eyes can see across the red sea to the rusty coloured mountains of Arabia.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/a4/21/b9/our-new-location-just.jpg', 'Eel Garden View Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/EelGardenViewRestaurantDahab/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(136, '3 El Malel Street, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', '(Eat in/Take Away/Delivery) BoxMeal works towards bringing appetizing satisfaction to both foreigners and locals of magical Dahab. Our kitchen was found on the basis of passion and love for cooking. We have been able to work towards offering our customers nothing but the best. We pride ourselves in the ability to work together like a family with the objective of making you feel like a part of it', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0f/7b/9a/af/20170516-191525-largejpg.jpg', 'BoxMeal', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Boxmeal/106731216470951', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(137, 'El Fanar Street, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Trendy, western-style healthy food restaurant and smoothie bar. 100% plant-based, serving organic ingredients locally sourced. The menu is seasonal and has a wide range of superfoods, daily freshly baked goods, raw cakes, and many gluten-free options. A green outdoor area with living plants and stable wi-fi is offered.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/16/6e/f6/e8/the-vegan-lab-entrance.jpg', 'The Vegan Lab', '4.5', 'http://www.instagram.com/thevegan_lab', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(138, 'Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'We operate a small Cafe to chill with good food, good vibes, and good people. We offer various types of food, parties and live music on some nights, hookah/shisha, and a relaxing chill environment. Come visit us for a genuine Egyptian experience and leave with Egyptian friends!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/10/d0/dd/8e/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Kung Fu Pasta', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/kungfupastadahab/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(139, 'Franks Rd, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Sababa hotel & restaurant have the best location in the middle of Dahab. Our hotel have sea view rooms. You can order in our restaurant 7 kind of delicious breakfast and Russian cusine. Try the best pizza, sandwiches and cakes in Dahab with us! Our restaurant have sunbeds by the Red Sea and easy sandy entry to Banner Fish reef. Welcome to Sababa!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/19/1b/35/5a/fresh-juices-from-sababa.jpg', 'Sababa Hotel', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/Sababa-hotel-Dahab-189729554705776', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(140, 'Mashraba Dahab South Sinai Egypt, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Our cuisine hosts many master chefs who enjoy and perfect the salient dishes we serve. Trust my word. Even our sous chefs are incomparable in their job. It is our strategy that your taste be satisfied. Lindy\'s Pantry and Restaurant enjoys the best of views as it does host the best of cooks and chefs. JAN 28TH', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1a/61/b9/af/best-food-in-dahab.jpg', 'Lindy\'s Dahab Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Lindys-Restaurant-Dahab/968290009968954', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(141, 'center of Dahab Mashraba Al Masbat, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Off the main drag in Dahab, but well worth a visit. You select your fish at the ice counter, and pay by weight. Much fresher, and much better value than the seafront restaurants. Rice, fries, vegetables, soup and mezze starter are all thrown in for the cost of the fish, so excellent value. Well worth a visit!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/02/20/2c/1a/absolutely-delicious.jpg', 'Sea Bride', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/%D9%85%D8%B7%D8%B9%D9%85-%D8%B9%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B3-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A8%D8%AD%D8%B1-sea-bride-%D8%BA%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A8-%D8%BA%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%85-938067539636106/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(142, 'Eel Garden Area Between Elprimo Hotel And Adam\'s House, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'A cozy tranquil place, with a colorful bohemian mood, and mouthwatering fresh homemade food. Kakao cafe & restaurant offers a range of sandwiches, salads cakes, drinks, besides some awesome delicious vegan stuff.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/63/ad/00/kakao-cafe.jpg', 'Kakao Cafe', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/kakaocafedahab', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(143, 'Beach Promanade Lighthouse Area, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Restaurant , Hotel and diving center find liberation,freedom and highest happiness while relaxing at our comfy restaurant right on the beach with delicious indian food , following the adventurous path diving the stunning dive sites in and around Dahab and in the end of the day falling asleep to the sound of the ocean', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/07/bc/27/d6/roof-top.jpg', 'Nirvana Restaurant', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Nirvana-Restaurant-557368351042090/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(144, 'Lighthouse Boulevard, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Cozy restaurant in the middle of town on the beachfront', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/21/64/76/27/hotel-lidia-outdoor-lounge.jpg', 'Lidia Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.lidiahoteldahab.com', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(145, 'El Melal Street Assalah, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Blue Beach Restaurant is situated on the shores of the Red Sea in the well known Blue Beach Club Hotel complex. We offer international and middle eastern fare in a relaxed environment. Our chef and staff look forward to being at your service!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/01/87/76/06/dahab.jpg', 'Blue Beach Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.bluebeachclub.com', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(146, 'First Right After Sina Market, Assala, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Seaduction is a Lebanese and International Restaurant/Caf‚ , located in assalah, Dahab. Join us and experience dahab as it should be.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/24/db/21/19/cafe-located-in-assalah.jpg', 'Seaduction Dahab', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/seaductiondahab', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(147, 'Dahab 069 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Kwanza cafe and restaurant is located at the center of dahab in the famous el mamsha with a diverse menu and cozy atmosphere.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/2c/6d/09/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Kwanza Restaurant & Cafe', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Restaurant/Kwanza-Restaurant-Cafe-110191736978833/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(148, 'El Masbat Street, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Jackie?s is not just a place to eat. Jackie?s is a way of life. We specialize in delicious, fresh, authentic Mexican food. And we also offer you a space to be, to learn, and to create.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/12/30/1b/0f/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Jackie\'s', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/Jackies-158113708131653', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(149, 'Lighthouse Area In Front Of Mahlawy Juice Bar, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Flavors for Royalty', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/27/0b/78/dc/flavors-for-royalty.jpg', 'Engenka', '5', 'https://web.facebook.com/Engenka/menu', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(150, 'El Masbat, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Green Valley offers you a large selection of typical egyptian food,barbecue and large range of fresh fish (make your one plate).It\'s situated on the nice promenade of Dahab, close to the famous Masbat bridge. We have very cosy tables seafront and also some typical bedouin seatings. My friendly staff and I would be pleased to welcome you any day of the week, to have a drink next to to the sea or to have a meal in a very good atmosphere...', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/03/55/17/de/green-valley.jpg', 'Green Valley', '4', 'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=306015643320532', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(151, 'El Fanar St. In front of Ceramic Cleopatra Exhibition, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'The best steaks in Egypt! At Grill House Restaurant, every mouthful is memorable. Offering a range of cuts including: T-bone, Fillet Mignon, New York and Sirloin Steaks served with a delicious array of sauces and sides. Main dishes include kofta, lamb ribs, tarb, chicken, mixed grills, pizza, pasta, soups and salads. The perfect spot for an evening amongst friends, romantic dinner for two or a memorable family dinner.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1c/5c/02/1d/new-menu-available-from.jpg', 'Grillhouse Restaurant', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/Alfanar-Grillhouse-Restaurant-752784725123089/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(152, 'Golden Europe Hotel, 1 Lighthouse, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'The Roof garden restaurant offers elite breakfast and dinner experience overlooking the magnificent views of Dahab\'s Bay. Enjoy chef\'s significant aromas, textures and flavors using the best of the local ingredients. Reservations are recommended for non Hotel guests.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/1d/1b/ee/00/the-roof-garden-restaurant.jpg', 'The Roof Garden', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/theroofdahab', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(153, 'Fanar street,, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'you can eat traditional korean and japanese food in Dahab, egypt . Enjoy aisan food with us and join us for enjoying dahab in our way Eat Dive Sleep and repeat!! That is how we do it!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/96/70/40/ddajo-asian-table.jpg', 'DDajo Asian Table', '4', 'https://www.facebook.com/ddajoasiantable/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(154, 'El Melal Street Blue Beach Hotel, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Steakout Dahab is an amazing memorable dining experience with exciting menus and relaxing atmosphere and warm hospitality. We take pride to source the best ingredients in the market to provide our customers with a variety of delicious and seasonal dishes. Our concept is built on the belief that food should be fresh and good quality produce cooked with a passion and value for money.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/22/cc/a6/39/steakout-dahab.jpg', 'Steakout Dahab', '3.5', 'http://steakoutdahab.com', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(155, 'Lighthouse Rd, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'The Holy Chef is an extraordinary restaurant in the heart of Dahab offering a wide range of delicious freshly prepared food, often giving a twist to well known dishes like Tacos or burgers with a unique flare from Executive chef Maha Khattab. Situated in the famous lighthouse area just steps from the beach the restaurant offers daily vegetarian and vegan dishes too in a calm welcoming environment. Upstairs is a chill-out zone where many come to enjoy the food and work on-line or look Down on the vibrant life of Dahab from the terrace. HTC has a passion for excellent food and hospitality.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/22/d0/b0/4b/street-view-of-thc-and.jpg', 'The Holy Chef', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/theholychef.thc', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(156, 'El Mashraba Street, Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Downtown Cafe is an Art Cafe that has been handmade from start to finish. Sit and enjoy the sea view with a hot or cold drink, a delicious slice of fresh cake and a shisha. There are drawings, paintings, carvings and more to look at, enjoy your time!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/19/e4/a0/73/downtown-cafe.jpg', 'Downtown Cafe', '3.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/downtowndahab/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(157, 'Dahab Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Antika is a restaurant and cafe at dahab we serve fried chicken plate sandwiches: burger ( beef & chicken), chicken all food is homemade and fresh included burger. we serve also hot drinks like: Coffee, espresso, and Cappuccino, sodas and juice.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/35/e4/12/amazing-place.jpg', 'Antika', '3.9', 'http://www.facebook.com/antika.cafe.resturant/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(158, 'Blue Hole Rd, Dahab 46617 Egypt', 'Dahab', 'Drift is a newly opened cocktail bar located at Dahab Paradise, offering the best view of Dahab by the Red Sea', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/2a/67/8d/6a/a-light-halloumi-tabouleh.jpg', 'Drift', '4', 'http://www.instagram.com/driftbar.dahabparadise/', 14, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(159, 'Downtown / Building H3, El Gouna, Hurghada 84513 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'The unique & authentic Swiss restaurant on the Red Sea. Join us in El Gouna! Swiss Cheese Fondue, Raclette, original Swiss Rost, the unique HotStone, \"Chasspatzli\", Veal Zuri Style, Tradtional cold cuts plate, Valais cheese slices and more. Enjoy the unique & authentic swiss food in El Gouna.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/24/d2/3b/2a/chuchichaschtli-swiss.jpg', 'Chuchichaschtli', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/swisshouse.elgouna', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(160, 'Abu Tig Marina, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Part of Captains Inn Hotel', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/84/54/ea/prachtig-uitgebreider.jpg', 'Captain\'s Steakhouse', '4.5', 'http://www.hotels.elgouna.com/captains-inn', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51');
INSERT INTO `resturants` (`id`, `address`, `city`, `description`, `image`, `resturant_name`, `rating`, `website`, `city_id`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(161, 'Abu Tig Marina, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Tandoor Restaurant boasts its new concept of unique and delicious Asian Fusion dishes that will tingle your senses. With it\'s great view, amazing cocktails and cozy ambience, the Far East has never been closer to you. Indian cuisine and Far East recipes carry intense flavours, and this re imagined interior sets the perfect tone of ease and comfort, Now the tone is set for an unforgettable culinary experience. The signature dish is Dum Biryani Lamb and it?s a real showstopper. Prepared with love by Tandoor?s resident Indian chef, the Biryani is cooked in a traditional clay pot (tandoor) to enhance the fusion of flavours', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/21/bd/b2/08/interior-tables-for-dinner.jpg', 'Tandoor Restaurant - Ali Pasha Hotel', '5', 'https://hotels.elgouna.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/TANDOOR-MENU-1.pdf', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(162, 'Inas El Degheidy St Downtown, El Gouna, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Inspired by the most magical places - Bongoyo Island... we promise to bring El Gouna a little piece of Culture, Fun & Food from the motherland AFRIKA with a ?K? :) Our flavors are meticulously crafted to fit every flavor palette while paying tribute to our roots. At Bongoyo we offer a variety food profiles that will take you on a tour from South Africa, Tanzania & Kenya all the way to Congo & Senegal. It?s an experience not to be missed. #TASTEAFRIKAN', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/20/f2/5e/59/welcome-to-bongoyo.jpg', 'Bongoyo Restobar', '5', 'http://www.bongoyorestobar.com', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(163, 'Rihana Resort Deluxe, El Gouna, Hurghada 84517 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Nicole?s Greenhouse is a helping hand into a greener community, here to heighten awareness of the food we consume and inspire eating more from the rainbow. Our nourishing dishes serve to satisfy your tastebuds in new ways you didn?t think possible in hopes of reinforcing daily conscious consumption that heals Earth, Mind, and Body. As people often say, what goes around comes around and we want better for all to come around. All menu items are vegetarian or vegan, made with passion and served with love.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/2a/e6/16/67/caption.jpg', 'Nicole?s Greenhouse', '5', 'https://ttcresorts.com/rihana-resort-deluxe/rihanna-green-house-restaurant/', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(164, 'Abu Tig Marina, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Le garage is a typical Burger Restaurant , but not a fast food restaurant, its located at the Marina of el gouna, nice Terrace with a fantastic view on the water. We serve a big variation of around 22 burgers, also for vegetarians, very nice salads, soups and filet steaks. Our daily freshly baked cakes are great too. The friendly waiters and chefs are all wearing a garage overall, suitable to the name \"le garage\" Please don\'t forget to write a comment on the restaurant walls. Free WLAN for all guests', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0b/3d/74/09/the-black-pearl-and-the.jpg', 'Le Garage - Gourmet Burger', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/pages/Le-Garage-Gourmet-Burger-El-Gouna/115165748550392', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(165, 'Downtown Building H17, Next to Go Bus station, El Gouna, Hurghada 84513 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Karibu means ?welcome? in Swahili. Situated in the heart of Downtown, Karibu is a favorite amongst kiters, locals and visitors offering a chilled atmosphere to hang out. We are known for our amazing Burgers and special nights including Steak Mondays and Family Dinner Wednesdays and on Tuesdays our Live music night attracts a fun crowd and feel good vibes.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/77/b2/1b/220g-beef-filet-parmesan.jpg', 'Karibu - Bar & Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.karibu-elgouna.com', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(166, 'El Gouna downtown Behind Crystal bike, H-11, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Looking for authentic Egyptian cuisine? Look no further than Kan Zaman. A fantastic little restaurant, with pavement tables, an AC interior, and an outside seating with a view across the square under the refreshing breeze of a couple of ceiling fans. You are always greeted with a warm welcome and shown to a beautiful decorated table. Kan Zaman is not only known around El Gouna for its great tasting Egyptian cuisine and great value, it is also known for their amazing customer service. You are shown a selection of both Egyptian favourites and some simpler options with generous portions whatever you choose. Fear not if you don?t understand the menu, the staff are all very experienced in dealing with customers who don?t quite know what to choose and have been proven to provide excellent advice on their dishes.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/27/22/4e/23/kan-zaman.jpg', 'Kan Zaman Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://elgouna.directory/pg/kanzaman-restaurant/', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(167, 'Opposite Ebeid Supermarket, El Gouna, Hurghada 00000 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Inspired by regional and traditional Latin American Cuisine, Chicha takes a modern approach to the authentic flavours of latin America. The menu is inspired through a fusion between Mexican and Peruvian Nikkei cuisine. Chicha is a Corn based Beer that is traditional to Peru, and is consumed in great quantities during and after the work of harvesting, making for a festive mood of singing & dancing. Here in Chicha we honour just that, and aim to make every day a celebration of Latin American flavours.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/17/a9/a7/0b/chicha.jpg', 'Chicha Restaurant & Bar', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/Chicha-Restaurant-Bar-420737882018924/?modal=admin_todo_tour', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(168, 'El Gouna Downtown Across the wooden bridge behind Ebeid Market, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Nestled in the heart of Kafr El Gouna by the lagoon, \"The Grill\" offers a large variety of deliciously prepared mezzas; succulent charcoal roasted chicken; savory grilled meat, kofta and quails; super tender and mouth watering fillet; and an array of scrumptious wraps, soups and salads. Alternatively our Vegetarian menu features authentic Aubergine Fattah; fulfilling Pasta Vegetariana; Egyptian lentil soup; and fire roasted vegetables; together with delicious list of well prepared salads. All our meals are served with baskets of our signature freshly baked brick oven bread. Choose from a list of well prepared cocktails, mocktails, wine and beer, and enjoy a scenic lagoon view or a cozy indoors area. The Grill is perfect for large groups and birthday celebrations, as well as intimate evenings. For Egyptian, Mediterranean and Oriental cuisine lovers, this restaurant is a must. The Grill is open daily from 1 pm till 11:45pm', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/26/6e/66/62/mix-grill-with-flame.jpg', 'The Grill el Gouna', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/theGrillelGouna/', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(169, 'Abu Tig Marina, El Gouna, Hurghada 14474 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'A unique dining experience right in the very heart of El Gouna - welcome to the home of quality - Breeze Restaurant & Bar. Enjoy generous portions of fresh mouthwatering food and relax, while admiring gorgeous Abu Tig Marina views.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/15/a1/99/11/home-of-quality.jpg', 'Breeze Restaurant & Bar - El Gouna', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/breeze.elgouna/', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(170, 'Downtown, Kafr, El Gouna, Hurghada 84513 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Puddleduck is a family-owned restaurant with an English accent. PUDDLEDUCK is not just a restaurant. It is a cozy and quiet corner of England in bustling Egypt. Not only do we serve meals, we give you a taste of childhood and a family atmosphere. We are generous and our plates are more than full. We are responsible, so we choose each ingredient for you personally. We are creative, so we are constantly expanding the menu and updating the interior. We are fans of our business so your food will always be delicious and interesting. Guests at Puddleduck are people who appreciate the quality of the dishes, the friendly service, and the cozy atmosphere of a family dinner. The menu of our kitchen presents the best dishes of English cuisine, prepared according to ancient recipes, with original English spices and sauces that we bring from misty Albion.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/27/9c/8f/3a/wishing-you-hope-peace.jpg', 'Puddleduck Bar & Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/puddleduckelgouna', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(171, 'Inas El Degheidy Street Down Town, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Welcome to Snack Shack, a cozy restaurant located in a small town called El Gouna, proudly serving up delicious eats since 2006. Home to a menu packed with mouth-watering foods, including our famous sweet waffles that are sure to make your taste buds dance. We also offer a variety of healthy options, sandwiches and wraps, juicy burgers and more. Pass by for some good eats and sweet treats.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/28/00/68/beef-bacon-burger.jpg', 'Snack Shack', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/thesnackshack.elgouna', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(172, 'Abu Tig Marina, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Mazagouna is Gouna\'s must-visit restaurant and bar, located right in the center of Abu Tig Marina. Offering a sumptuous selection of Lebanese and Egyptian dishes with exquisite cocktails Shisha is also served here.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/13/3d/5a/8f/fattoush-come-try-our.jpg', 'Mazagouna', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/mazagounaofficial/', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(173, 'Kafr Kh 26 Opposite Credit Agricole / Girges Supermarket, El Gouna, Hurghada 84513 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'NEW IN TOWN LA PLAYA combines a great beach, gorgeous outdoor seating and a large air conditioned inside room, serving breakfast, lunch, beach snacks and fine dining. Located in the heart of Kafr El Gouna, LA PLAYA is the new trendy hangout.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/19/0a/1b/e0/beautiful-decor-down.jpg', 'La Playa', '5', 'http://www.laplaya-elgouna.com', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(174, 'Abu Tig Marina, Mb 10-1 between Breeze And Lawrence, El Gouna, Hurghada 00000 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Inspired by Regional and Traditional Asian Cuisine, Barten takes a modern approach on the flavours of Asia offering fixtures like Sushi and Ramen in addition to a wide variety of appetizers and bar classics and creations', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1c/62/30/87/sushi-selection.jpg', 'Barten - Sushi Restaurant & Bar', '5', 'http://www.instagram.com/barten.elgouna/', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(175, 'Fk-38 Kafr Elgouna, El Gouna, Hurghada 84511 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Overlooking the lagoon in the heart of El Gouna (Kafr, downtown), our restaurant offers Italian cuisine, specifically Pasta and Pizza made with exclusively handmade dough and high quality products, Open every day, the restaurant offers private spaces for events, parties, aperitifs. We offer home delivery services We observe all standards of protection and prevention against Covid-19 for our staff and customers.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/26/8e/2e/c5/entrance-pasta-e-basta.jpg', 'Pasta e Basta', '5', 'http://facebook.com/pg/pastaebastakafrelgouna/menu/', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(176, 'El Balad, Downtown, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'We were recommended this restaurant for its good food, cheap price - and that it didn\'t make its patrons sick (other restaurants in Downtown El Gouna don\'t share that reputation!) I\'ve seen it mentioned on other Trip Advisor postings as a recommendation for eating in El Gouna - would really recommend it as it was great food and very popular!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/05/b7/4b/21/white-elephant-thai-resturant.jpg', 'White Elephant Thai Resturant', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/pages/White-Elephant-Thai-restaurant/312496925453050?fref=ts', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(177, 'Abu Tig Marina, El Gouna, Hurghada 11122 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'In the scenic Abu Tig marina you can sit and have a breakfast, lunch or dinner and watch the people or the million dollar yachts pass by. Menu is typical international seafood with both vegetarian and other options available. New for January 2012 is the Volcanic Rock Grill where you grill your own dish at the table (available from 6pm)', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/02/71/3f/68/maritim-restaurant.jpg', 'Maritim Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://maritim.elgounarestaurants.com', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(178, 'In Front Of Mosaique Hotel, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'On the boardwalk of Mosaique Hotel', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/22/2e/0e/26/mer-bey.jpg', 'Mer Bey', '5', 'http://www.mer-bey.com', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(179, 'Tamr Henna Square, El Gouna, Hurghada 84513 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'The only sportsbar in town with typical barfood and BBQ. Watch your favorite sports on request.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/15/50/3f/85/jobo-s-sports-bar-during.jpg', 'Jobo\'s Sports Bar & Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/Jobos.Sports.Bar/', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(180, 'Unnamed Road, El Gouna, Hurghada 84513 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'The best Oriental & International cuisine starting from Shish Tawok to the best steaks in town. Best refreshing drinks served in ElGouna', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/2a/29/6a/c9/caption.jpg', 'Maroush ElGouna', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/maroushelgouna', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(181, 'El Gouna Downtown Next to ebaid market downtown elgouna, El Gouna, Hurghada 84513 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Kirvem steakhouse was founded by Ezzat Girgis in 2013 on the principles of fresh, authentic food made by hand. Steaks would be hand-cut, ribs would fall off the bone, the sides made from scratch. No shortcuts, just real food made fresh daily. full service, casual dining restaurant. We offer an assortment of specially seasoned hand-cut steaks and fall-off-the-bone ribs cooked to order over open gas-fired grills, Hot stone. In Addition to steaks, we also offer our guests a selection of ribs, fish, seafood, chicken, vegetable plates, and an assortment of hamburgers, salads, and sandwiches.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/22/e8/b9/1d/ostrich-steak.jpg', 'Kirvem Hot Stone Steak House', '4.5', 'http://www.kirvemsteakhouse.com/', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(182, 'New Marina, El Gouna, Hurghada 84513 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'We serve healthy food for body & soul. Lots of superfoods, smoothies, desserts, fresh salads, quiches, tarte flambee (flammkuchen) freshly made sandwiches with our homemade fresh baguettes, as well as soups. They say we have the best cake and coffee . We have a very nice outdoor sitting on both sides of the Deli, in the summer it is never too hot to sit on our Terrace, there is always a nice breeze at the Piazza side. Our guests love our all day breakfast. You can find us on the big piazza at Abu Tig Marina. Malu\'s Deli is under management of The Deli Company of Switzerland.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/12/43/78/23/fresh-smoothies.jpg', 'Malu\'s Deli', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/Malus-DELI-El-Gouna-133951603641431/timeline', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(183, 'Abu Tig Marina, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Moods (El Gouna, Red Sea, New Cairo) is a well-established project since 2003. We specialized in the food and beverage, tourism industry. When it comes to Egyptian soothing experiences, we are considered one of the exquisite destinations mixing between all what the family needs and what the youth desires. We are famously known for being a landmark in El Gouna, Red Sea, for it is the purpose designed for all those who want to enjoy a delightful, restful yet liveliness time for a genuine, beautiful mood shift. In 2017 we introduced Moods to New Cairo when we opened our branch there bringing the same quality to town. Planned by the way it is, Moods was able to be the hub for all those who seek a unique, exclusive way of entertainment especially those who are seeking a sandy and pleasant time or those who look for the warmth of family outings and quality time.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/e0/4f/c9/moods-restaurant-beach.jpg', 'moods Restaurant & Beach Club', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/Moods.ElGouna?refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMoods.ElGouna', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(184, 'Abu Tig Marina, El Gouna, Hurghada 84513 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Lawrence El Gouna Restaurant offers oriental food such as the famous tagine and chicken on charcoal, as well as kofta and meat on charcoal and offers famous Syrian dishes, hot drinks and alcohol', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/21/80/f7/24/lawrence-el-gouna-restaurant.jpg', 'Lawrence El Gouna Restaurant', '5', 'http://lawrence-restaurant.business.site/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=referral', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(185, 'El Gouna, Hurghada 84511 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'El Sayadin, located directly on the shores of the Red Sea with breathtaking views over the turquoise water is a unique restaurant built in authentic style of a wooden fisherman hut. A fine dining restaurant with seafood dishes, ?Catch of the Day? selection from the Red Sea, prepared to guests? liking, local specialties from the Oriental Grill and an exquisite selection of desserts for an outstanding culinary experience.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/8d/1c/e6/el-sayadin-restaurant.jpg', 'El Sayadin Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://all.accor.com/hotel/B4L7/index.en.shtml?dateIn=2021-12-30&nights=1&compositions=2&stayplus=false#origin=accor', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(186, 'Red Sea New Marina, El Gouna, Hurghada 84513 Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'The official page for both beautiful outlets in El Gouna overlooking the stunning views of the Red Sea. The Smokery Beach and El Gouna Yacht Club.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/21/8f/26/01/exclusively-tucked-away.jpg', 'The Smokery El Gouna Yacht Club', '4.5', 'http://www.thesmokeryrestaurants.com', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(187, 'Mb13-04 Abu Tig Marina, El Gouna, Hurghada Egypt', 'El Gouna', 'Welcome to Boho Cafe! We create our dishes in a fusion culinary style which combines aspects from Middle & Far East with fresh produce and full bodied flavors with a contemporary twist.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/27/83/c0/a1/boho-cafe.jpg', 'Boho Cafe', '5', 'http://instagram.com/bohocafe.elgouna?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=', 18, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
