(191, '1 Galaa Square, Dokki Sheraton Cairo Hotel & Casino, Giza 11246 Egypt', 'Giza', 'Sapporo, a city in Japan famous for its culinary scene and brewing beverages and fresh seafood was the main inspiration behind ?Sapporo Restaurant? the vibrant Japanese restaurant well known for its fresh Sushi menu and teppanyaki choices at the Sheraton Cairo Hotel. Our Famous Sapporo restaurant was the first Japanese restaurant to offer Teppanyaki and Sushi in Egypt back in the 90s, then closed for renovation as part of the hotel extensive renovation in 2011 and now is back with a revamped space to offer daily fresh authentic sushi, teppanyaki and Japanese dishes, fueled by a live DJ performance and a buzzing bar. Sapporo is now headed by the Japanese chef ?Komatsu? who also comes from the city of ?Sapporo? in Japan. Komatsu joined the Sapporo team in the 90s, which was his first job in a hotel restaurant in Egypt and now he is back again after so many years to where he belongs. Let the Show Begin!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/5b/ce/bd/sapporo-s-team-is-waiting.jpg', 'Sapporo Japanese Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/sappororestaurantcairo/', 25, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
