(211, 'Cornish Road, Jabal Al Harim Adjacent to Hilton Plaza Hotel, Hurghada 84511 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Solo Restaurant & Lounge opened its doors earlier this year and has already gained its reputation of bringing the very best of International cuisine and hospitality to the heart of Hurghada. Visit us now and you get to see the restaurants new look! Where all our customers are invited to dine in style in a beautiful location full of ambience. Our menu altern both Egyptian and International cuisine, Fresh quality meat, barbecued grills, seafood, salads, pasta and oven baked dishes. We work hard to include local sourced and seasonal ingredients in all the dishes we serve. So we can guarantee we will leave your tastebuds tingling and your stomachs wanting more! So if you are looking for a fine dining experience, mouthwatering food, the very best service, a fancy cocktail / mocktail or even a place to chill whilst listening to a selection of your favorite music. Then Solo Restaurant & Lounge is the place to be!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1a/cb/1a/ea/solo-restaurant-lounge.jpg', 'Solo Restaurant & Lounge', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/SoloHRG', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
