(218, 'Sheraton Street, in front of Dream Beach, Hurghada 84511 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'What does the name of the restaurant mean? The name Sardinia goes back to the pre-Roman name ?Sard? (in Latin Sardus and its feminine form Sarda). It is believed that this name has a religious connotation because it was also used as an adjective for the god-hero Sardus Pater, ?the Sardinian father? from Sardinian mythology. Sardinia was called \"Ecnosa\", which is the Latin word for the Greek \"Hyknusa\". It was also called Sandaleon, Sardinia and Sardu by the Greeks and Romans. What does our restaurant offer? Our restaurant offers a small but varied menu that satisfies all tastes. It varies between Grill and steak also pasta , pizza with some types of soup, salads and appetizers. We also serve breakfast, lunch and dinner. Advance reservation is preferred. We await your visit and are happy to serve you.and looking forward ,,to make sure that your happy and that you you will back again to visit us , and you will recommend our restaurant for your family and friends,see you when you visit', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/28/34/ed/21/happy-valentines-day.jpg', 'Sardinia Grill & Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/sardinahome', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
