(224, 'Hurghada Marina Boulevard, Hurghada 84514 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'New American steakhouse and caf‚ at Marina boulevard in Hurghada. We serve you the best steaks, burgers, ribs and gamba\'s in town. Also for a nice drink from our bar you are very welcome. You will find us at one of the most beautiful spots of Hurghada. The view is amazing and the athmosphere is relaxing. We are also ready for your birthday party or other big events in your life.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/2a/b5/fb/38/caption.jpg', 'Las Vegas American Steakhouse Restaurant & Cafe', '5', 'http://lasvegas-hurghada.com/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(225, 'Intercontinental Behind Al Haya Hospital, Hurghada 84511 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Located in intercontinintal district, Bostan lounge offer you a modern ,unique atmosphere and relaxing dining experience indoor our outdoor , with several TV screens for any sports you like to watch, Our kitchen service you generous portion off our home favorites freshly cooked to order. Cold Beer is always waiting for you with big selection of soft and hard drinks.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/21/a4/df/a8/getting-ready-for-christmas.jpg', 'Bostan Lounge', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Bostan-Lounge-101676975079024/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(226, 'Corniche Arabia Azur Resort, Hurghada 5555 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'The first Restaurant of the Bordiehn\'s chain, opened 1991. Celebrating 25 th anniversary soon, unique sitting open air, with fireplace, performance stage with daily changing program, separate romantic dining by candle lite,offers kids friendly , vegetarian and meat lovers dishes, special price scheme for Azur Hotel guests available.We invented the famous and unique dish\"Camel Tenderloin with Chocolate chillie Sauce\"new inventions like Buffalo steaks give it a try.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/02/80/08/3c/villa-kunterbunt.jpg', 'Bordiehn`s Villa Kunterbunt', '4.5', 'http://www.bordiehn.org', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(227, 'Sheraton Road Bella Vista Building, Hurghada 84511 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Caribbean Beach Bar Smooth Soul, progressive bossa, rock ballads and real deep house combined with cool drinks, fresh salads and grilled delicacies, guarantee summer feeling pure,surrounded by the awesome scenery of the Red Sea. During the day, you can drink a cappuccino here, in the afternoon it can be a cocktail in a relaxing lounge atmosphere. And always enjoy the beautiful view and atmosphere, which exudes casual elegance and internationality. All in all a good mix of fine dining and rustic lounge bar, spiced with demanding club music. The Caribbean change after dinnertime to the hot spot location of the party scene.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/03/79/29/f9/caribbean-bar.jpg', 'Caribbean Bar', '4.5', 'http://Www.Facebook.com/CaribbeanBar', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(228, 'New Marina, Hurghada 11511 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Stone is a modern European restaurant with a swiss touch,we are the only place in hurghada that makes tasty cheese fondue and Spatzli,we serve amazing cocktails and ice cold beer,an amazing sea view with wicked bean bag seating area,the entrance of marina where you can see all boats and yachts coming and going,Shisha', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/09/f5/6f/c8/grilled-chicken-sandwich.jpg', 'Stone Restaurant & Bar', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/stonerestaurantandbar/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(229, 'Senzo Mall, Hurghada 84511 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Texas & Mexican Restaurant Welcome to the Chili\'s Hurghada - in SENZO MALL, a place where you can spend time with your friends, your family, and the ones you love the most like no place else!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1f/95/94/31/logo.jpg', 'Chili\'s Hurghada', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/chilishurghada/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(230, 'Hurghada Marina, Hurghada 84517 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'The Lodge is all about diverse, good quality, European food. While specializing in great steaks with a unique extra taste from the charcoal grill, there is also an extensive selection of Vegetarian and Fish courses. The Lodge uses only fresh, high quality food, this together with the comfortable, warm ambiance makes for an ideal dinning experience.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/03/43/41/7c/the-lodge-restaurant.jpg', 'The Lodge Restaurant', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/TheLodgeRestaurantBar/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(231, 'Corniche Road Next Sunrise Holidays-, Hurghada 84511 Egypt', 'Hurghada', '\"The Tavern Bar is located now at the heart of Hurghada, Red Sea, Egypt, THE TAVERN Hurghada concept brings a new premise to the nightlife entertainment offer in this dynamic tourist hotspot.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/2a/91/be/26/caption.jpg', 'THE TAVERN Hurghada Restaurant & Pub', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/THETVERN.HRG', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(232, 'Tawaya, Old Town, Sahl Hasheesh Bus Stop Sahl Hasheesh, Building F, Hurghada Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Day & Night, Beach & Lounge, Elegant & Casual, Lively & Relaxed, Family Friendly & Adult Only, Every thing at its right time. We?re located on the beautiful bay of Sahl Hasheesh directly on the Boardwalk & the Sandy Beach. Bus Stop is a well known Egyptian brand since 1987, famous as a restaurant, sports bar & lounge. Eat & D Our cuisine is fundamentally comfort food however we care for every taste including vegan and vegetarian options. We serve variety of cocktails, Detox fresh fruits & vegetables, smoothies, wine, beer & the best milk-shakes in town. We air live HD sports, boast the best pool table in the region, premium darts, foosball and video games. Music is the main essence of the Bus Stop experience. We?re really into our Live Music but also in-house DJs? select our daily playlists. Groovy Soul, Commercial, Pop, Revival, RnB, Dance are regulars to our music menu but you also have the choices from the extensive collection of music, music-videos, karaoke & our Custom Jukebox.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1d/02/26/fc/ribeye-steak.jpg', 'Bus Stop Sahl Hasheesh', '4.5', 'http://www.busstopsahlhasheesh.com', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(233, 'Sheraton Rd., Hurghada Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Star Fish is one of the biggest seafood & fish restaurant in the red sea, serving you with delicious & tasty choices of fish & seafood platters, which you can choose on which way it can be cooked. Our chefs makes sure to serve you with most delicious platters and amazing cooking recipes which will sure take your heart & soul. make sure to give Star Fish a visit while you\'re enjoying the amazing Hurghada City Available now Two branches for Star Fish Sheraton Branch Sahl Hasheesh Rd Branch', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0c/9a/2c/e5/prima-zeker-een-aanrader.jpg', 'Star Fish Restaurant', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/starfishrestaurant1', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(234, 'New Marina, Hurghada Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'From the heart of Rome to beautiful Hurghada, L\'Imperatore is the most authentic Italian dining expe', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/29/f4/e5/97/restaurant-bar.jpg', 'L\'Imperatore Marina', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/LImperatoreMarinaHurghada/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(235, 'Sheraton Road, Hurghada Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'I Have Ask For This Restaurant Before As I Find It One Of The Best In Town And Have Had No Response', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0a/27/7e/97/20160121-103103-largejpg.jpg', 'samos', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/pages/Samos/166819190118739?fref=ts', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51');
