(236, 'Siva Mall, El Mamsha, Hurghada Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Mandarine and Aladdin Lebanese Restaurant & Orient Cafe. A dining room remarkable for its appeal to the eye... Setting, good cooking and reasonable.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/05/db/27/67/mandarin-lebanese-resturant.jpg', 'Mandarin Lebanese Resturant', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/pages/Lebanese-Restaurant/191593151756614', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(237, 'SUNRISE Garden Beach Resort, Hurghada 84517 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'A unique sense of serenity, beauty, and taste welcomes you at the Nasaya Beach Lounge and Restaurant. Drink your favorite beverage during the day and taste the delicious entries of food we have to offer in the evening.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1b/fe/a4/23/nasaya-at-sunrise-garden.jpg', 'Nasaya Restaurant & Lounge', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/nasayarestaurantandlounge/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(238, 'Behind Nara Cafe El Kawther, Hurghada Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'English Tea Room & Cat Cafe. Enjoy a fine cup of tea or coffee, home made cakes and biscuits and at the same time cuddle with our feline family. Breakfast, lunch & afternoon tea on offer. Limited outdoor seating for smokers.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/09/c8/b3/61/the-purrfect-cuppa-english.jpg', 'The Purrfect Cuppa English Tea Room', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/PurrfectCuppaHurghada/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(239, 'El Corniche Road Hurghada Marriott Red Sea Resort, Hurghada Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Serving fine Northern Italian cuisine including grilled meat and fish specialties.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/09/fb/49/58/ristorante-tuscany.jpg', 'Ristorante Tuscany', '4.5', 'http://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/hrgeg-hurghada-marriott-beach-resort/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(240, 'Youssef Affifi Street Road, El Mamsha Siva Mall, The Mall of Siva Grand Beach Hotel, Hurghada 84511 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Welcome to Gaucho Steak House Restaurant, where we\'ve served the finest Argentinean-style steaks since 1999. Our menu features a premium selection of aged beef cuts, grilled to perfection and served with various traditional Argentinean sides. We are also proud to offer an extensive wine selection. Our restaurant is located in Hurghada, Red Sea, Egypt, providing the perfect setting for a memorable dining experience, special events, and private dining.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/03/81/39/5c/gaucho-steakhouse.jpg', 'Gaucho Steakhouse', '4.5', 'https://www.gaucho-hurghada.com', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(241, 'Village Road Next to Sindbad Club Hotel, Hurghada Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'The sister venue to Little Buddha Bar Paris- Little Buddha Hurghada opened its doors in 2008 to welcome everyone to dine and drink in this unique and luxurious venue. Our number 1 priority is service to our guests with a very large number of them returning again and again, this is done with understanding that each guest is imperative to the continued success of our venue. With this in mind we strive to meet the individual needs of everyone. The Dining Experience A unique mix of imaginative contemporary Asian, Japanese, French, Pacific and Sushi food, opulent interiors and exotic world music Little Buddha is one of the most exciting and impressive restaurants. A full a la carte menu with exotic delicacies and luxurious dishes, With highly qualified chefs specializing in each genre of food. Warm friendly efficient front of house staff trained to elevated standards, whether we are catering for individuals, couples families or large groups. We endeavor to stay close to our core belief to cater for each individuals needs. The Nightlife Experience Home to some of Egypt\'s best resident DJ and host to some of the world best guest DJ that set the dance floor on fire. A complete change from the relaxed and sophisticated dining experience that we offer, Little Buddha becomes an energetic stylish background for a mix of both tourists and prestigious VIPs looking to enjoy the chic, electric atmosphere. The right atmosphere, the right music, the right staff and the right clientele is what makes Little Buddha.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/26/da/b6/fb/party-time.jpg', 'Little Buddha', '4', 'http://www.instagram.com/littlebuddhahurghada/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(242, 'Sheraton Street beside McDonald?s, Hurghada 84511 Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Our restaurant is located in the downtown of Hurghada. We have Italian, Egyptian and International food. A varied weekly party (music - guitar - oud - flute). very comfortable and relaxing decor', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/ab/58/b4/love-this-place.jpg', 'Bucks Restaurant & Cafe', '4.5', 'https://m.facebook.com/bucksrestaurants/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(243, 'El Kawther, Metro Street Next To Tiger Store, Hurghada Egypt', 'Hurghada', 'Japanis cosine and sushi restaurant visit us and enjoy our delicious sushi and blhanna w alshefa??????', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/29/99/ec/f6/caption.jpg', 'Sumo sushi', '5', 'http://www.facebook.com/sumosushi.eg/', 26, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(244, 'Al Rawda Al Sharifa Street, Luxor 85951 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'It is a restaurant that serves the best grills of the finest meat If you are a supporter of tajines, then meat tajines, okra, akkawi, mambar, and others are available to you in various types and with the best taste. If you are from the category of eaters, or from the category of those who follow the diet, then your destination is Loqma, to get the right meal for you that will not only satisfy you, but also make you feel happy. Loqma is one of the best restaurants in Luxor, which offers you what you desire in terms of food, according to your expectations and aspirations in the required meals, and may even exceed them in many cases.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/28/31/e1/bd/caption.jpg', 'Loqma Restaurant', '5', 'http://loqmarestaurant.com', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(245, 'St Joseph Street,, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'A Taste Of India & Arabia International Restaurant Plus Lounge Bar is Luxor\'s premiere Asian & Arabian Restaurant we serve quality Indian & Middle Eastern Cuisine with a good International Menu plus our great steaks & Burgers. Our COCKTAIL & COFFEE LOUNGE is NOW OPEN. The restaurant & Bar is fully licensed featuring ICE COLD bottled beers, Draught Heineken, a good wine list, spirit and cocktail selection plus fresh ground Lavazza coffee with additional flavor shots, all available in the main restaurant or in our lounge area whether dining or not. Restaurant is NON SMOKING(6pm TO 10pm) From 10pm we have \"AFTER HOURS\" Supper Club & Bar with it\'s own bar menu and Full Bar Service. Look out for my new restaurant HARD WOK CAFE Chinese & Thai Food', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0d/87/eb/27/russell-owner-a-taste.jpg', 'A Taste of India & Arabia International Restaurant Plus Bar', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/tasteindialuxor/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(246, 'Dr Labib Habashy Street, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'It has moved into the former \"Oasis Cafe\" building, across from the Bank of Misr. Please call ahead to arrange free transportation.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/f6/ca/c5/oasis-palace.jpg', 'Oasis Palace', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/PizzeriaTerrazzaFiera/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(247, 'Khaled Ben El Walid Street Steigenberger Nile Palace Hotel, Luxor 85111 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'At Steigenberger Nile Palace, we are pleased to welcome you to our Thai Restaurant. Enjoy our extensive … la carte offer with a mouthwatering range of traditional Thai flavors. The atmospheric design of the Thai Restaurant is inspired by the Thai heritage and our Thai Chef will be happy to welcome you, explain the authentic specials, advice and create the perfect dishes while you enjoy a romantic view over the river Nile and the Theban Mountains from the terrace.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/21/64/81/8a/sawasdee-and-welcome.jpg', 'Thai Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.steigenberger.com/hotels/alle-hotels/aegypten/luxor/steigenberger-nile-palace/restaurants-bars', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(248, 'Kaled Ebn Elwaled St. First Floor Front of Sonesta Hotel & Lotus Hotel & Steigenberger Hotel, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', '\"SunRise\" is a modern Restaurant & Bar, a place where you will find the perfect balance of Oriental and European ambiance. A la carte menu offer a range of local, Italian, vegetarian and international dishes and snacks including the traditional Sunday-Roast. Enjoy your time with us a little longer and make a choice from our beverage list with alcoholic or non-alcoholic cocktails and drinks while watching the English Premier League and All live sport Matches, an amazing sunset, happy hour from 5:00 to 6:00 pm, using our complimentary WIFI. Enjoy your holiday With \"SunRise\" and join our karaoke, live band & live show parties. The familiar atmosphere at \"SunRise\" will make you feel at home and we will be happy and proud to serve you and make a contribution to your perfect day and vacation. Hope to see you soon!!!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/15/cf/a7/b3/sunrise.jpg', 'SunRise Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/sunriseluxor', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(249, '90 Mohamed Farid Street Al Manshiya, Luxor 83911 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Ahlan wa sahlan in Sofra, a restaurant located in the heart of Luxor that draws its inspiration from the rich Arabian culture. Sofra is situated in an old 1930s Egyptian house that still retains its traditional character. Sofra: A culinary voyage through Egypt! Discover the secrets of Egyptian cuisine and enjoy true traditional food in an oriental atmosphere in the heart of Luxor, Egypt.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/daodao/photo-m/1280/16/85/a8/cc/nice-food.jpg', 'Sofra Restaurant & Cafe', '4.5', 'http://www.sofra.com.eg/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(250, 'Gezira Al Bharat West Bank, Luxor 85951 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Your favourite waiter from the Africa Restaurant (Ahmed/Adam) has taken his expertise and experience and opened his own restaurant specialising in traditional Egyptian Food, like Mama makes. The house specialities are Stuffed Roast Quail, Camel Meat Tagine and Stuffed Roast Duck', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/15/2f/6f/d8/the-best-egyptian-food.jpg', 'Sunflower Restaurant West bank', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/SunflowerRestaurant1', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(251, 'El Rawda El Sharifa St. Front of Sonesta Hotel, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Brand new establishment, fully , experienced and professional staff, fresh ingredients daily.,. Aisha is Luxor\'s the most popular Egyptian and English restaurant and a favourite of guests from all around the world.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/28/56/27/9d/lovely-group-and-great.jpg', 'Aisha Restaurant Luxor', '5', 'http://aisharestaurant.business.site/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=referral#gallery', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(252, 'El-Mahdi Street on the corner of St. Joseph Hotel Opposite street of sonesta hotel, Luxor 71111 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Situato in una zona tranquilla vicino ai maggiori hotel. Arredamento semplice ma con colori caldi alle pareti , cucina a vista.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/22/d6/1a/b8/pizza-diavola.jpg', 'Pizza Roma-it', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/pages/Pizza-Roma/512966385389330', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(253, 'Khaled Ben El Walid Street, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'At Steigenberger Nile Palace, we are pleased to welcome you once again in our hotel. The health of our guests, employees and partners is our highest priority. We would like to ensure our guests that we are taking every precaution to keep you safe and comfortable. The Steigenberger Nile Palace takes pride in pampering her guests with top quality cuisine, based on the notion that culinary highlights are an essential element in every vacation. The unique, international culinary creations from our kitchens meet the expectations of the world travelers with our \'Nubia\' international buffet restaurant, Lebanese \'El Tarboush\', Italian \'Casa di Napoli\', Steigenberger Thai, Gourmet restaurant \'The View\' and Barbecue Terrace \'Nile Plaza\'. For guests who would like to have a \"quick bite\", we offer menus at Caf‚ des D‚lices, the Nile Lounge Bar and Terrace and the Pool Side Bar \'Tropicana\'.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/31/ac/5e/mixed-grill-at-el-tarboush.jpg', 'Steigenberger Nile Palace Luxor Restaurants', '5', 'http://www.steigenberger.com/en/Luxor/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(254, 'Al Roda Al Sharifa Street, Luxor 85836 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'We are a busy English Restaurant serving English food and some International/Egyptian Dishes, with a specials board that changes daily. Fully licensed bar with great air conditioning.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/08/87/41/96/the-lantern-room.jpg', 'The Lantern Room Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/The-Lantern-Room-Restaurant-in-Luxor-218632264864470/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(255, 'Khaled Ben El Walid Street, Luxor 85111 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'At Steigenberger Nile Palace, we are pleased to welcome you once again in our hotel. The health of our guests, employees and partners is our highest priority. We would like to ensure our guests that we are taking every precaution to keep you safe and comfortable. The Steigenberger Nile Palace takes pride in pampering her guests with top quality cuisine, based on the notion that culinary highlights are an essential element in every vacation. The unique, international culinary creations from our kitchens meet the expectations of the world travelers with our Lebanese Restaurant \'El Tarboush\', \'Nubia\' international buffet restaurant, , Italian \'Casa di Napoli\', Steigenberger Thai, Gourmet restaurant \'The View\' and Barbecue Terrace \'Nile Plaza\'. For guests who would like to have a \"quick bite\", we offer menus at Caf‚ des D‚lices, the Nile Lounge Bar and Terrace and the Pool Side Bar \'Tropicana\'.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/21/2a/79/b1/casa-di-napoli-at-steigenberge.jpg', 'Casa Di Napoli', '5', 'https://www.steigenberger.com/hotels/alle-hotels/aegypten/luxor/steigenberger-nile-palace/restaurants-bars', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(256, 'El Rhoda El Sherifa St El Rhoda El Sherifa St Luxor Egypt, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Located in the heart of the magnificent historic city of Luxor, Egypt. Snobs Restaurant serves the best English, International, Egyptian and Vegetarian Cuisine.Freshly delivered, daily prepared and cooked with the best ingredients to the highest standards of hygiene by an expert professional team. Managed by chef Moamen who worked at the royal guests palace in Saudi Arabia and has cooked for the Saudian king and most of the international Heads of State from around the world.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/25/a8/fb/17/snobs-grand-mezzs.jpg', 'Snobs', '4.5', 'http://snobsrestaurant.com', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(257, '21 El Gwazat Street, Luxor 83951 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'We are a small takeaway and serve inexpensive and authentic Thai food. Open Monday to Thursday from 1 to 9 pm. Sunday we cook in the Gezirah Garden Hotel on the West Bank.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/09/f1/21/a7/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Kam Thai Takeaway', '4.5', 'http://kam-thai-takeaway.jimdo.com/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(258, 'Kornish Al Nille Luxor Governorate On The Nile In Front Of The Sofitel Winter Palace, Luxor 85111 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'If you are looking for a taste of real Egyptian cuisine, look no further than El-Kababgy restaurant in Luxor. This cozy place offers a variety of dishes that are cooked with fresh ingredients and traditional spices. You can enjoy Mashi, a stuffed vegetable dish, tagines, slow-cooked stews with meat and vegetables, grill specialties such as Shish Tawook, chicken skewers, Kebab and Kofta, minced meat patties, and more. Don\'t miss the Hammam, pigeon with rice, Fatta, bread with meat and sauce, Mesaka\'a, baked eggplant with cheese, and Feteer, flaky pastry with sweet or savory fillings. All this while admiring the stunning view of the Nile and the West Bank of Luxor from the restaurant\'s terrace. El-Kababgy is a must-visit for anyone who loves Egyptian food or wants to try something new and delicious.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/25/39/e8/6d/el-kababgy-luxor.jpg', 'El-kababgy Luxor', '5', 'http://elkababgyluxor.com/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(259, 'Al Bairat Al Qarna, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Nubian typical food recipes prepared with pigeons, rabbits, ducks, fishes, chickens and regular meat. We have wood oven to cook some meals. Also, come to try our mint tea.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1c/c7/53/e5/photo4jpg.jpg', 'Nubian House Restaurant', '4.5', 'https://nubianhouse.business.site/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(260, 'Ramla West Bank, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Seasonal food cooked freshly for you. Soups, salads, tagines, using fresh herbs. Great for vegetarians and vegans. A large selection of drinks, including our popular fresh juices. Healthy and delicious. Also special events featuring art, music and dance. Very easy to find from the ferry.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1e/6b/ff/2a/surround-yourself-with.jpg', 'Wannas Art Cafe', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Restaurant/Wannas-art-cafe-113682926709765/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(261, 'JJ_s at El Gezira Gardens Hotel El Gezira Hotel Gezira-el-Beirat. West Bank, Luxor LU1 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Our Story as of 08-08-2020 We opened JJ\'s Bar & Restaurant in Karnak, Luxor on the 12th January 2009 after a two year build. After 8 years of business and two revolutions - JJ\'s Bar & Restaurant moved to El Gezira Hotel, Geziret-el-Beirat, West Bank, Luxor and re opened on the 1st September 2017, where we operated from the top floor restaurant and bar and ground floor garden. On Thursday 8th February 2018 we moved to El Gezira Gardens Hotel. Due to the world Coronavirus pandemic we closed on Wednesday 19th March 2020. During early August we relocated back to El Gezira Hotel and opened up again on Saturday 8th August 2020 where we provide our daily specials board, a good selection of beers and wines and organise theme nights, live music and regular entertainment. We hope you\'ll find time to visit JJ\'s when you\'re next on the West Bank in Luxor JJ?s at El Gezira Hotel, Geziret-el-Beirat, West Bank, Luxor Home to the Rock ?n? Ra Burger JJ\'s Bar & Restaurant voted Egypt\'s Best Bar &', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1b/ed/4a/61/jj-s-roof-top-bar-and.jpg', 'JJ\'s Bar and Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.jjsbargezira.weebly.com', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(262, 'Hilton Hotel, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Treat your taste buds to a fine dining experience in exquisite surroundings at the elegant Silk Road. Explore exotic eastern cuisine, savoring an array of delicacies from all over Asia, such as delicately spiced Indian curries and aromatic Malaysian soups.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1d/ed/26/a5/silk-road-restaurant.jpg', 'Silk Road Restaurant', '4', 'http://www1.hilton.com/en_US/hi/hotel/LUXHITW-Hilton-Luxor-Resort-Spa/dining.do', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(263, 'Khaled Ben El Walid Street Steigenberger Nile Palace Hotel, Luxor 85111 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'At Steigenberger Nile Palace, we are pleased to welcome you once again in our hotel. The health of our guests, employees and partners is our highest priority. We would like to ensure our guests that we are taking every precaution to keep you safe and comfortable. The Steigenberger Nile Palace takes pride in pampering her guests with top quality cuisine, based on the notion that culinary highlights are an essential element in every vacation. The unique, international culinary creations from our kitchens meet the expectations of the world travelers with our Lebanese Restaurant \'El Tarboush\', \'Nubia\' international buffet restaurant, , Italian \'Casa di Napoli\', Steigenberger Thai, Gourmet restaurant \'The View\' and Barbecue Terrace \'Nile Plaza\'. For guests who would like to have a \"quick bite\", we offer menus at Caf‚ des D‚lices, the Nile Lounge Bar and Terrace and the Pool Side Bar \'Tropicana\'.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1e/56/a7/ee/nile-lounge-bar.jpg', 'Nile Bar and Lounge', '5', 'https://www.steigenberger.com/en/hotels/all-hotels/egypt/luxor/steigenberger-nile-palace/restaurants-bars', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(264, 'New Karnak Hilton Luxor Resort & Spa, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'With beautiful, contemporary interiors inspired by the Rosetta Stone, this relaxed main restaurant at the Hilton Luxor Resort & Spa features both banquette seating and cozy booths for intimate dining. Begin the day with a famous Hilton breakfast and a glass of exotic fruit juice as you overlook the Nile.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1d/ed/11/e7/rosetta-restaurant.jpg', 'Rosetta Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www3.hilton.com/en/hotels/egypt/hilton-luxor-resort-and-spa-LUXHITW/dining/index.html', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(265, 'Ramla West Bank, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Rooftop dining on the west bank of Luxor, serving modern Egyptian cuisine, local beers and wines, vegan and vegetarian and amazing organic lamb, chicken and beef burgers.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/28/7a/e9/b9/caption.jpg', 'Thebes Bar And Grill', '5', 'http://thebesrestaurant.com/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(266, 'Cornesh El Nile Street Khaled Ibn Al Walid, Gazirat Al Awameyah, Luxor 1362003 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'The main dining room features natural light and views of the Nile River and pool, serving buffet breakfast, lunch and theme dinners featuring Continental, International, Japanese and Egyptian cuisine.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/23/c3/b2/45/main-restaurant.jpg', 'Sonesta St. George Hotel - Luxor Restaurant', '4.5', 'https://www.sonesta.com/sonesta-hotels-resorts/luxor-governorate/luxor/sonesta-st-george-hotel-luxor', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(267, '38, Khaled Ibn Alwaleed Street - al Awamea between Isis and Achti Resort hotels, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Our Restaurant Maxime was created in 1995 by Sara (French) and her husband Mahmoud (Egyptian). We have 2 floors: 1st non-smoking - 2nd authorized smoker. After your dinner, you can enjoy our EL SALTANA coffee-shop connected to Maxime. For disabled people, meals prepared by Maxime\'s Chefs can be served at EL SALTANA which is located on the ground floor.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/01/bc/0e/ed/humm-quel-regal.jpg', 'Maxime Restaurant', '4', 'http://maxime.web361.fr/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(268, 'Al Qarnah, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Welcome to the Paris Cafe! We are here to welcome you to Egypt the best way we know how. Come and visit the Colossus of Memnon (walking distance) and the Valley of the Kings (30 min away) and eat the same foods as the Pharaohs. Chicken and Beef Shawarma, Lamb Tagine, fried fish served with choice of potatoes, salad, pitta bread and our House special Kufta sauce. Welcome and Enjoy!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1a/13/d7/34/e.jpg', 'Baris Cafe', '5', 'http://www.thebariscafe.com', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(269, 'St Joseph Street, Luxor 235689 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Here You Will Find A Relaxing Atmosphere Home From Home Comfy Sofa Area And Also Table Dining Area We Welcome All Families Too Child Friendly With Very Friendly Staff .all Home Made Cooking To Suite Everyone Scones Apple Pie Etc Plus Evening Steaks Burgers ..', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/16/b5/02/2a/cosy-and-welcoming.jpg', 'Tutti Frutti  Restaurant', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2042620629130522&id=546628398729760', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(270, 'Near the Temple of Medinat Habu IN Luxor Malkata House, Luxor 85111 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'By reservation only - good food is just the beginning at restaurant Malkata House. As well as eating dishes prepared by the best chef in Luxor, you will enjoy a magnificent atmosphere.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/23/10/7b/f6/enjoy-a-delicious-dinner.jpg', 'Malkata House', '5', 'http://inluxor.com/restaurant', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(271, 'Market Street Right in the souk, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Jamboree Restaurant opened in 1997. It has everything you want to see from the views you like. We have free wifi. Support your decision and visit us, you will not regret. Thanks for people who give us their time to help us.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/01/57/cb/6b/new-om-kalthom-coffee.jpg', 'Jamboree Restaurant Luxor', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/Jamboree-Restaurant-at-LuxorEgypt-289947028515260', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(272, 'Medinet Habu West Bank, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Habou Garden Restaurant is a family run business owned by Ahmed Mohamed (Ahmed Luxor) and managed by his brother Mohamed Ahmed. Other members of the family are a part of the friendly and welcoming staff. The restaurant is well known for serving delicious Egyptian and Western food and has been operating for many years. We have recently had a face-lift and change of name. Habou Garden was formerly known as Hapy Habou Restaurant. The name has changed but the welcoming and friendly service, and delicious food have not changed. If you have enjoyed times at our restaurant in the past, please visit us again and please tell all your friends to come and visit us, to enjoy the Habou Garden experience. Just down from Medinet Habu Temple, and right opposite the Sacred Theban Hills (home to the Valley of The Queens and Kings etc), this is a very ancient and Sacred area. We invite you to enjoy not only our family restaurant, but the complete Sacredness of the Theban Hills.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/3b/3d/d7/view-from-thecar-and.jpg', 'Habou Garden', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/Habou-Garden-Restaurant-106218630792076/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(273, 'Khaled Ben El-Waleed Street Gazirat Al Awameyah, Luxor 85111 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Situated at the Steigenberger Nile Palace Hotel in Luxor, an authentic Thai restaurant, where Thai Chef Umar will welcome the guests and prepare a culinary adventure. Enjoy your dinner inside a beautiful, air-conditioned setting or at the terrace with spectacular view over the river Nile and Theban Mountains.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/2d/cb/15/steigenberger-nile-palace.jpg', 'Restaurants & Bars at Steigenberger Nile Palace', '4.5', 'https://hrewards.com/en/steigenberger-nile-palace-luxor/restaurant-bar', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(274, 'El Rawda El Sharifa St. In Front Of Layaly Zaman Cafeteria, Luxor 95851 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Newly refurbished, under new management and name \'Castello Restaurant & Cafe\' New menu, fresh ingredients daily. why Chef Castello ?? Because Chef Castello She won the gold medal in the chef competition Organized by IMAGE International Also she holds a silver medal This is not a void The chef has many years of experience in restaurant chains and large and international hotels Quickly Come and visit our outstanding restaurant and chef And who will honor you and your friends and your guests And you will meet the high quality and the distinguished service here In Castillo ??? And the title is MyTouch Al-Awamiya next to CIB Bank In front of Hotel Steigenberger #Castello_ sufficient # Eat_On us', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/17/b3/a3/d8/castellorestaurantnet.jpg', 'Castello', '4.5', 'http://castellorestaurant.net', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(275, 'El Asayta St. Behind the Tourist Information Building, Luxor 85951 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'organic ice cream 20 flavor at least of ice cream Frappuccino very tasty & Italian coffee 100% all juices are fresh 100% soft music so kindly staff', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/19/5d/ff/bc/caption.jpg', 'Philadelphia Ice Cream', '4.5', 'http://www.facebook.com/Philadelphia-Ice-Cream-Taste-it-419588828178039/?ref=bookmarks', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(276, 'West Bank, Qurna, Near to the Ramesseum, Luxor 85831 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Restaurant with freshly prepared food and fresh fruit juices, soft drinks and a range of hot drinks. All round view from the shaded roof-terrace over the Tombs of the Nobles, the Mortuary Temple of Tuthmosis III, and the agricultural land. Air-conditioned restaurant on the first floor with panoramic windows. Micro-buses stop outside and their is ample on and off-street parking. Very near the Ramesseum. We are open from 11:00 every day.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/15/f7/6a/1b/seen-in-the-glow-of-the.jpg', 'Panorama Restaurant and Cafe', '5', 'http://panorama-luxor.weebly.com', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(277, 'El Ramla Street Al Bairat, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Luxor', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/28/27/54/4e/caption.jpg', 'La Plage Cafe', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100063936335034', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(278, 'Corniche El Nile Street, Luxor 85957 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Beban is our signature restaurant with spectacular views of the Nile and the hotel swimming pool from large panoramic windows located on the first floor. Serving … la carte Italian specialties and a wide range of beverages in an intimate setting.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/24/23/1b/9d/beban-restaurant-overview.jpg', 'Beban Italian Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.sonesta.com/sonesta-hotels-resorts/luxor-governorate/luxor/sonesta-st-george-hotel-luxor/', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(279, 'New Gourna Street, Luxor Egypt', 'Luxor', 'The name says it all: Makany means my place. To make you feel at home is our motivation. Fully air conditioned, our tasty drinks and high quality shishas make our place a comfortable area to relax.The perfect place to spend a good time with your family and your friends.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/17/25/8d/68/makany-cafe.jpg', 'Makany Cafe', '5', 'http://www.makany-luxor.com', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(280, 'Corniche El Nile Street, Luxor 85957 Egypt', 'Luxor', 'Miyako presents Japanese cuisine. The restaurant?s Japanese design creates an elegant dining atmosphere; with private dining room and a Tatami room for intimate gatherings, while the open seating area offers Teppan Yaki tables for a larger group of 10. Authentic Japanese and Asian fare is freshly prepared using genuine Japanese ingredients.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/24/23/1e/4a/japanese-and-asian-food.jpg', 'Miyako Japanese Restaurant', '4', 'http://www.sonesta.com/luxor', 29, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(281, 'Marsa Alam Road TUI SENSIMAR Alaya, Madinat Coraya, KM 65 El Quseir, Marsa Alam Egypt', 'Marsa Alam', 'The food of Italy is certainly among the most visually striking in the world, such reached its culinary height and outstanding reputation long before the 20th century. We have selected a few dishes from each Italian province and hope you enjoy our culinary trip.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/19/c7/fc/2b/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Basilico Italian Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.jazhotels.com/marsa-alam-madinat-coraya/hotels/TUI-Sensimar-Alay.aspx?fbclid=IwAR2o8YiJ6K9330dRiKOfATykBuZd-hqEN-zzLkpC__8sXtscdlbxqL4Lz4w', 31, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(282, 'Port Ghalib Port Ghalib marina, Marsa Alam Egypt', 'Marsa Alam', 'hakuna matata cafe and restaurant at Port Ghalib Marina, Port Ghalib Marsa alm Red Sea , it\'s one of the best places at port ghalib we will always be waiting for you and it\'s a pleasure to serve you don\'t worry be hakuna be happy', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/13/a2/fd/a2/port-ghalib-marina-with.jpg', 'Hakuna Matata Restaurant & Cafe', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Hakuna-Matata-cafe-589703531365242/', 31, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(283, 'Marsa Alam Road TUI Sensimar Alaya, Madinat Coraya, KM 65 El Quseir, Marsa Alam Egypt', 'Marsa Alam', 'ROKA?s concept is based on a modern Izakaya, a culinary sharing experience originated from Japan. Our menu in ROKA is a culinary journey through Asia?s cuisine, covering a number of countries. We hope you enjoy this as much as we do.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/61/15/49/photo3jpg.jpg', 'Roka Asian Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.jazhotels.com/marsa-alam-madinat-coraya/hotels/TUI-Sensimar-Alay.aspx?fbclid=IwAR2OUUc3hSQcPtaQ23tNTjH7nV2t0j3w-Ac1_VeP866inzRDnvjSSACvYG8', 31, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(284, 'km 67 El Qusier, Marsa Alam Road Madina Coraya, Marsa Alam 84721 Egypt', 'Marsa Alam', 'momo restaurant offer delicious and remarkable food and drinks. That the food and drink meets the highest standards of quality. To consistently provide our customers with impeccable service by demonstrating warmth, graciousness, efficiency, knowledge, professionalism and integrity in our work.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/00/83/d3/feuer-darf-nicht-fehlen.jpg', 'momo Asian Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/MoMo-Asian-Restaurant-2149236261840534/', 31, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(285, 'Port Ghalib, Marsa Alam Egypt', 'Marsa Alam', 'Nubian Restaurant and caf‚', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/25/c9/34/24/rayga-cafe.jpg', 'Rayga Cafe', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Hurghada.2017.me/?ref=page_internal', 31, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(286, 'Madinat Coraya, 67 KM El Qusier, Marsa Alam Egypt', 'Marsa Alam', 'Sofra restaurant offer delicious and remarkable food and drinks. That the food and drink meets the highest standards of quality, freshness and seasonality and combines both modern-creative and traditional southern styles of cooking. To consistently provide our customers with impeccable service by demonstrating warmth, graciousness, efficiency, knowledge, professionalism and integrity in our work.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/27/7e/ec/e6/caption.jpg', 'Sofra', '5', 'http://www.jaz.travel', 31, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(287, 'Madinat Coraya, Km 65 El Quseir TUI Sensimar Alaya, Marsa Alam Egypt', 'Marsa Alam', 'At ZAYTOUN we would like that our guests get to experience typical oriental traditions by embodying the essence of the region, which is embedded in culture, warmth and hospitality. The food at ZAYTOUN comes from recipes deeply rooted in Egyptian, Palestinian and Lebanese heritage, offering a wide selection of tapas-like communal dishes to be shared.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/19/fd/21/67/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Zaytoun Middle Eastern Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.jazhotels.com/marsa-alam-madinat-coraya/hotels/TUI-Sensimar-Alay.aspx', 31, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(288, 'Marsa Alam Road TUI Sensimar Alaya, Madinat Coraya, KM 65 El Quseir, Marsa Alam 84721 Egypt', 'Marsa Alam', 'The CULINARIUM is one of the most beautiful seafood restaurants on the Red Sea, to enjoy life to the fullest. Here chef Durmus Uzun and his team conjure up an atmosphere in which you can enjoy different delights in a wonderfully relaxed manner.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/19/c8/00/9a/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Culinarium Sea Food Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.jazhotels.com/marsa-alam-madinat-coraya/hotels/TUI-Sensimar-Alay.aspx?fbclid=IwAR2o8YiJ6K9330dRiKOfATykBuZd-hqEN-zzLkpC__8sXtscdlbxqL4Lz4w', 31, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(289, 'Marsa Alam Road The Three Corners Fayrouz Plaza Beach Resort, Marsa Alam Egypt', 'Marsa Alam', 'The art of cooking receives the highest emphasis at the Chez Pascal Restaurant. The Chez Pascal Restaurant offers an authentic Belgian cuisine with a choice of steaks cooked to perfection, seafood and lobster dishes.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/26/e6/33/af/crepes-suzettes-mit-vanilleeis.jpg', 'Chez Pascal Restaurant', '5', 'http://threecorners.com/red-sea/fayrouz-plaza-beach-resort/dining/resturants/', 31, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(290, 'Al Qusair - Marsa Allam Road Jaz Grand Marsa Hotel, Marsa Alam Egypt', 'Marsa Alam', 'For years and years Aladdin has been flying around on his magical carpet in search for a perfect place to settle down for good, and he has finally found it on the Red Sea shore, a marvelous place for endless nights full of fairy tails and splendor. Meet charming princess Jasmine and whisper your wishes to the Genie released from his magical lamp. Welcome to Aladdin Restaurant & Lounge.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/26/19/71/81/aladdin.jpg', 'Aladdin Restaurant & Lounge Bar', '5', 'https://www.facebook.com/alsultan.aladdin/', 31, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(291, 'outside Al forsan hotel, Mersa Matruh 51511 Egypt', 'Mersa Matruh', 'We serve zalabya a traditional Egyptian desert with toppings of your choice, we also serve fries with out secret seasoning and we have the best waffle in town', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0d/7e/d7/0c/caption.jpg', 'Potato & Zalabya', '4', 'http://www.facebook.com/Potatoandzalabya/', 32, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(292, 'Almaza Bay, Mersa Matruh 5058510 Egypt', 'Mersa Matruh', 'Located just steps away from Almaza Bay beach, Sachi Almaza\'s key focus is the bounty of the sea. The menu inspired by the Mediterranean Coast and the North Coast rough environment celebrates the simple pleasures in life, friends, food, and fun. The design is inspired by the coastal tones of the mediterranean and tranquil aesthetics of Southern Europe.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/2a/1d/73/56/sachi-almaza.jpg', 'Sachi Almaza', '4', 'https://www.sachirestaurant.com/sachi-almaza', 32, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(293, 'Almaza Bay Almaza Bay Beach Front,, Mersa Matruh Egypt', 'Mersa Matruh', 'Mediterranean seafront restaurant & bar with serviced beach area located in the magical Almaza Bay.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/24/22/df/27/enjoying-the-cookery.jpg', 'The Cookery Co.', '5', 'http://www.instagram.com/thecookeryco/', 32, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(294, 'El Salam Road, Nabq Bay, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Nabq Bay', 'Hard Rock Cafe is a global phenomenon with 185 cafes that are visited by nearly 80 million guests each year. The first Hard Rock Cafe opened on June 14, 1971, in London, England, and from there the brand has expanded to major cities and exotic locations around the world.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0e/42/3a/95/thisishardrock.jpg', 'Hard Rock Cafe', '4.5', 'https://www.hardrockcafe.com/location/nabq/', 59, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(295, 'El Salam Road La Strada Mall, Nabq Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 41000 Egypt', 'Nabq Bay', 'We combine the delights of a cold drink (or two), the satisfaction of filling food and the endless entertainment provided by screening the biggest matches, pool table, darts and more, to make The Bus Stop Zone your home away from home. Our family friendly lounge is decked out with the comfortable couches and we play all your favourite songs all day long or check the Karaoke and Live music nights. Feeling a little home sick? Come and get the finest pub grub, burgers, Sunday Roast, we serve it all with a smile. Feeling like listening to Live music or dancing, check for our schedule from RnB to Top of the Pops hits.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/36/ac/ba/bus-stop-nabq-your-local.jpg', 'Bus Stop Nabq', '4.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/busstopnabqbay/?_rdc=1&_rdr', 59, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(296, 'Portsaid Beach, Port Said Egypt', 'Port Said', 'Cafe And Restaurant And Beach @ Port Said City Cafe And Restaurant And Beach @ Port Said City Cafe And Restaurant And Beach @ Port Said City', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/27/de/2f/c0/nice.jpg', 'Bubble Beach Port said', '1', 'https://www.facebook.com/bubbleportsaid/', 35, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
