(298, 'Doaiah Beach, Port Said 42511 Egypt', 'Port Said', 'Thank you for contacting Doaiah Beach! Please let us know how we can help you. We Proudly Offers Private Beach Kids Area Entertainment Beach Music & Live Oriental Parties Water Sports Courses kitesurfing , Windsurfing , Kayaks , SUP Boards , Beach Volleyball Restruant & Cafe Serving Italian & Egyptian Cusines as Pizzas , Pastas , Fresh Juices , Special Coffee & All Hot and Cold Drinks', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1a/26/6b/ae/doaiah-beach-only-one.jpg', 'Doaiah Beach & Kite Club', '3', 'https://www.facebook.com/Doaiah.Beach/', 35, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(299, 'Soma Bay Safaga Road Qesm Safaga, Safaga 84711 Egypt', 'Safaga', 'A devotion to opulence naturally includes an unparalleled fine-dining experience. Throughout the day, the Laguna Club Lounge presents FIVE culinary delights and a host of luscious beverages, from simple to sensational, for your taste buds to indulge in. *The prices are including drinks and tax.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/24/f6/b5/fa/laguna-club.jpg', 'Laguna Club Lounge', '5', 'http://www.kempinski.com/en/soma-bay/hotel-soma-bay/hotel-facilities/laguna-club-lounge/', 42, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(300, '8 Kilo, Safaga 84711 Egypt', 'Safaga', 'Our cozy restaurant with terrace is open daily from 6 pm and offers a variety of dishes. Our chef cook and his team pamper you with fresh fish, meat & the specialties of the Orient and many other delicious dishes. Whether vegetarians, vegans, fish or meat lovers, in the PANORAMA RESTAURANT, the food for everyone is a treat!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/10/09/cc/38/es-ist-eingedeckt.jpg', 'Panorama Guesthouse & Restaurant', '5', 'http://panorama-safaga.com/', 42, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(301, 'Safaga Road, 55 Km Red Sea, Safaga P.O. Box 84911 Egypt', 'Safaga', 'Arabesque Lebanese Specialty Restaurant ? specializing in Oriental and Lebanese authentic cuisine, with selected signature dishes from the Levant, a wide range of mezzeh and grilled items served to perfection.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/29/56/73/71/caption.jpg', 'Arabesque', '5', 'http://steigenberger.com', 42, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(302, 'Safaga Road, 55 Km Red Sea, Safaga P.O. Box 84911 Egypt', 'Safaga', 'Cabana Pool-side Restaurant ? serving … la carte lunch or dinner array from Italian and Mediterranean specialties, a sunken bar with fresh cocktails and mocktails, small nibbles and tapas.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/29/b8/1c/d4/gluten-free-pizza.jpg', 'Cabana', '5', 'http://steigenberger.com', 42, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
