(320, 'Naama Bay mall number 6 Naama Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Step into the imaginative Mahony cave restaurant for an evening of seafood & fish specialities and steak house. Located in Naama Bay behind the Pyramid Mall on Peace Road, just next to the New Duty Free shopThe service is warmly welcoming and attentive. If you enjoy fresh seafood with an oriental flavour and well cooked herb chicken, lamb and beef fillets, skewered and served on a bed of fluffy rice, this is definitely a place for you. Not forgetting the atmosphere and decoration that is totally unique.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/22/d5/f7/1d/great-start-of-your-dinner.jpg', 'Mahony Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.mahonysharm.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(321, 'M”venpick Resort, Naama Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Kababgy fuses five-star Swiss service with Egyptian traditions of hospitality. Enjoy smart-casual dining in exquisite surroundings whether you choose to be seated indoors in the laid-back ambiance of Arabic interiors or outdoors with a breathtaking view of Naama Bay. Indulge in rich flavors of charcoal-grilled meats marinated according to time-honored recipes and variety of local delicacies!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/11/8a/4e/93/taking-pride-in-culinary.jpg', 'El Kababgy', '5', 'https://www.movenpick.com/en/africa/egypt/sharm-el-sheikh/resort-sharm-el-sheikh/restaurants/restaurants/el-kababgy/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(322, 'Soho Square, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'The Queen Vic is the traditional British local pub, where English native guests feel at home thanks to the design, atmosphere, the look & feel of the pub. Football matches are displayed on screens/T.V during the English football tournament /season. There\'s plenty of room with a long bar, indoor tables, chairs and booths. The Queen Vic serves a wide variety of beers, wines, and non-alcoholic beverages. The front of the Queen Vic is always open, leading out to the large wooden terrace, with outdoor tables and seating overlooking SOHO Square, also providing darts and a billiards room to enjoy with your friends.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/03/c7/a6/26/beer-garden.jpg', 'The Queen Vic', '4.5', 'http://www.soho-sharm.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(323, 'Camel Hotel, Centre of Naama Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'PROBABLY THE MOST FAMOUS BAR in Sharm El Sheikh! Camel Bar serving extensive dinner and drinks menus, including cocktails and shooters. Free wi-fi is available. THE ROOF: chill out with long drink and a shisha and admire the spectacular views of Naama Bay. Our drinks menu offers beers, local and imported wines, imported spirits, cocktails and shooters. DON\'T MISS: daily drinks promotions, Happy Hour and Weekends Sports Specials. Whether it?s a night out with the lads, watching the sports with a beer, cocktails with the girls, lining up shots on the bar or singing the night away, the Camel Bar is a iconic symbol of what happens when the sun goes down here in Naama Bay.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/1d/2f/1f/de/enjoy-the-sinai-s-warm.jpg', 'Camel Bar & Rooftop, Sharm El Sheikh', '4.5', 'https://www.cameldive.com/food-and-drinks-camel-bar-rooftop/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(324, 'Al Sultan Qabos-Mashaba La Strada Nabq Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 46911 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Located in the beautiful Nabq Bay Sharm el Sheikh you can enjoy a relaxing dining experience with indoor and outdoor seating. Sample our freshly made authentic Chinese dishes made using locally sourced ingredients.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/27/e5/d5/6f/mango.jpg', 'Mango Chinese Restaurant', '5', 'http://www.66mango.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(325, 'Soho Square, Sharm El Sheikh 169 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Traditional Cantonese (Chinese) meals created with oriental herbs and spices that have been imported especially to SOHO SQUARE to fully experience the dishes, with the natural ingredients that stimulate taste, sight and aroma. The authentic atmosphere of China is right there at Zen restaurant. Dress Code applies for men: no shorts, no flip-flops', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/03/a7/dd/81/zen.jpg', 'Zen Chinese Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.soho-sharm.com/sharm-restaurant-Zen', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(326, 'Domina Coral Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'The Beach Luxury Club is an exceptional beachfront restaurant offering culinary delights prepared with perfection. Delicious food, impeccable service, incredible dinner shows, amazing sea view and energizing DJ music offers a unique experience not to be missed.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/1c/b0/a2/79/the-beach.jpg', 'The Beach Luxury Club', '5', 'http://www.thebeachluxury.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(327, 'Soho Square Sharks Bay, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Authentic Thai cuisine served in an appealing oriental setting. Choose from spicy appetizers, such as the famous Tom Yum shrimp, chicken soup, various salads to start the meal, and they are fully indulged in Thai\'s finest tradition cuisine. Dress code applies for men: no-shorts, no flip-flops', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/06/ae/ad/de/mai-thai.jpg', 'Mai Thai', '4.5', 'http://www.soho-sharm.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(328, 'Sultan Gardens Resort Shark\'s Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 111 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'The newest addition to the Sultan Gardens Resort dining options; this exciting new outlet, serving Indian Cuisine, benefits from a central location, eye catching designs and stunning menu which are sure to make it an instant favorite.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/06/45/12/c7/dishes.jpg', 'House of Spice', '5', 'http://www.sultangardens.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(329, 'Mohammed Al Yamani, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Pasta and pizza by italian chef mauro only italian product italian fresh pasta hand made delivery and take away.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/29/7f/c2/88/i-propretari.jpg', 'Da Mauro Solo Pasta & Pizza', '5', 'http://www.damauropastaepizza.it', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(330, 'Soho Square, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'The mood and the menu at our Egyptian restaurant is as rich as the history of Egypt itself. At Luxor restaurant, there is a selection of cuisines to tempt any appetite; an appealing, great grilled meat selection and specialties, together with aromas and spices from the banks of the Nile. Traditional flavours and wholesome vegetables made for a banquet fit for a Pharaoh. Offering unique ways of cooking the finest local ingredients and all combinations are brought together with traditional Egyptian hospitality, touch and feel. Dress code applies: no-shorts, no flip-flops', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/04/89/61/a9/luxor.jpg', 'Luxor', '5', 'http://www.soho-sharm.com/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(331, 'Soho Square White Knight Beach, Sharm El Sheikh 169 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Teppanyaki is a word meaning \"Iron griddle\" (Teppan) and \"Fry\" (Yaki). Teppanyaki flare show and excellent cooking are developed into a highly refined and beautiful form of expression, characterized by an intricate combination of presentation and knife skills.\" The Japanese invented Teppanyaki, delicious, fast and very tasty. Start with a salad and a soup and then choose from four different menus: seafood, lamb or beef, or half & half. You will love the exciting Teppanyaki experience and the lively chefs demonstrating their expertise on the Teppan. Code applies: no shorts, no flip-flops', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/2a/98/70/9e/teppanyaki.jpg', 'Teppanyaki', '4.5', 'http://www.soho-sharm.com/sharm-restaurant-Sushi-Bar-_-Tepanyaki', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(332, 'Soho Square, Sharm El Sheikh 169 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Bombay Indian restaurant with our gourmet chef Tilakraj from Delhi, who demonstrates his wholehearted devotion to Indian food and the tandoori oven. Imported Indian sauces such as melonin masala or jawatri powder are used in different sauce-based dishes, such as Karachi gosht, with tender lamb cooked in a rich and delicious sauce. The menu also includes vegetarian options. Dress code applies for men: no-shorts, no flip-flops', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/04/89/62/b6/bombay.jpg', 'Bombay', '4.5', 'http://sharm-city.com/soho-bombay/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(333, 'Soho Square White Knight Beach, Sharm El Sheikh 169 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'L\'Entrecote, the finest restaurant, the classic French Style brasserie restaurant with the finest beef imported from Britain, Ireland, Australia and Japan, cooked on an open grill to your liking, served with Chefs secret recipe sauces or steak butters, the largest wine selection in Sinai, choose from balcony, or spacious booth seating, and attentive service; just bring your friends for a superb continental styled evening Dress Code applies: no shorts, no flip-flops', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/29/d1/54/62/we-are-located-at-soho.jpg', 'L\'Entrecote Steak House', '4.5', 'http://www.soho-sharm.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(334, 'Sultan Gardens Resort Shark\'s Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 111 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'The atmosphere will transport you to Italy and the food, highlighted by the best anti pasta buffet this side of Rome and homemade pastas and pizza to die for, will keep you coming back for more.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/05/8a/e5/7b/italian-delights.jpg', 'Casa Mia', '5', 'http://www.sultangardens.com/en/content-page/restaurants/32', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(335, 'Shark\'s Bay, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'The View Lounge is an ideal panoramic place, where you can watch the sunset, have an overview of SOHO SQUARE and overlook the Red Sea and Tiran Island. As soon as the sunsets, the SOHO lights start to glow with a kick into the nightlife. Relax in the modern LED furniture and enjoy the spectacular view!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/06/b0/fe/6f/view-lounge.jpg', 'View Lounge', '5', 'http://www.soho-sharm.com/sharm-restaurant-Viewlounge', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(336, 'Movenpick Resort, Naama Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', '\"Rangoli\" is the most popular Indian restaurant in town where you can enjoy delicious traditional Indian dishes Savor the creations during dinner of our Indian Chef serving tender meat and seafood directly from the hot embers of the tandoor, accompanied with soft, fresh & hot naans and rotis; all in an inviting atmosphere with panoramic view over Naama Bay', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/03/08/30/4a/rangoli.jpg', 'Rangoli', '5', 'http://www.movenpick.com/en/africa/egypt/sharm-el-sheikh/resort-sharm-el-sheikh/restaurants/restaurants', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(337, 'El Soultan Qabous Street, Na\'Ama Bay, South Sinai Na\'ama Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Hard Rock Cafe is a global phenomenon with 185 cafes that are visited by nearly 80 million guests each year. The first Hard Rock Cafe opened on June 14, 1971, in London, England, and from there the brand has expanded to major cities and exotic locations around the world.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/05/0e/85/a9/yummy.jpg', 'Hard Rock Cafe Sharm El-Sheikh', '4', 'http://www.hardrock.com/cafes/sharm-el-sheikh/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(338, 'Centre of Na\'ama Bay Camel Dive Club & Hotel, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'In the heart of Naama Bay\'s pedestrian area,  our Italian inspired restaurant serves top quality breakfast, lunch and dinner. Enjoy Mediterranean cuisine, fresh and flavourful seafood, home-made pasta & pizza, wide choice of imported alcohol, and more in our restaurant in the heart of Naama Bay. Under the expert guidance of our culinary artist and authentic Italian chef Guiseppe, our team of Chefs uses only the finest and freshest produce when creating our dishes. Handmade pastas, sauces, wood fired crispy pizzas, meats and seafood are only a few of the delights our menu has in store for your eating pleasure. The restaurant has a cool modern air-conditioned interior, while Pomodoro\'s terrace is cooled by fans in summer, and heated in winter - the perfect spot for people-watching while enjoying a delicious meal al fresco.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/1d/b3/7a/be/seafood-pasta-featuring.jpg', 'Pomodoro', '4.5', 'https://www.cameldive.com/food-and-drinks-pomodoro-restaurant/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(339, 'Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', '(FISHERMAN RESTAURANT) fisherman restaurant is it for seas foods . we created and built since 1985 in old market but for the devlopment this area our location become in amazing view specially after sahaba mosque build ... our new location in 30th of june garden .. we introduce the best taste of sea foods over sharm elsheikh .. we are cooking also the best type of sea food soup we have a good team of staff (the clever cheifs and waiters).. the restaurant have big parking for cars and ready for disabled', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/26/c8/42/08/caption.jpg', 'Fisherman', '4.5', 'http://wa.me/201090191681', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
