(341, 'Om El Seed Street Salah Taher Street, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'The best place in Sharm for all your occasions,birthday,anniversari,wedding,childrens birthday. We have children menu\',special men—\' or buffet for large number of guest. We will satisfy your request as our own. The original Italian restaurant serve fresh fish,Italian pasta,pizza,salades also on the beach. Enjoy With us', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/0e/ea/f6/44/beach-area.jpg', 'Reef Beach Restaurant Managed by Egyptian Vacation Club', '4.5', 'http://www.evcresorts.com/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(342, 'Soho Square Sharks Bay, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Traditional English afternoon tea is served in true British style with a wonderful range of tea, including Earl Grey, English Breakfast tea and Organic Japan Classic, Red Berries, Lemon Sky, Black Decaffeinated, Assam and Darjeeling, all served with delicious cakes & snacks.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/03/ce/20/7a/salon-de-the.jpg', 'Salon de The', '4.5', 'http://www.soho-sharm.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
