(344, 'Naama Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 46628 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Buddha Bar Sharm Offering a fusion of Pan-Asian and International flavors with opulent surroundings and oriental & eclectic beats, Buddha bar Sharm is a unique dining and nightlife destination for the discerning guest.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/23/3c/3d/01/buddha-bar-sharm-elsheikh.jpg', 'Buddha Bar', '4.5', 'http://www.buddhabar-eg.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(345, 'Il Mercato Street, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'For the love of food; Striving to offer something new and delicious in Sharm El Shiekh, we founded Tejano\'s Grill House, the first restaurant in the city with a menu inspired by the TexMex cuisine, offering you a variety of choices to suit both your taste and your budget with an emphasis on TexMex dishes along with quality prime cuts of a variety of meats presented with unique flavours, starting with our super slow cooked superstar beef brisket to all the way to perfectly grilled entrecote steaks and hunky hand-crafted beef burgers!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/13/0e/e2/f9/getlstd-property-photo.jpg', 'Grill House Il Mercato', '4.5', 'http://grillhouse-sharm.business.site/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(346, 'Na\'ama Center, 2nd floor, King of Bahrain Street, Sharm El Sheikh 11381 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Finest Lebanese Cuisine Since our Establishment in (2008) in our branch in Sharm El Sheikh , we have been honored to host thousands of guests from Egypt , Arabian countries and abroad, presidents of nations, local & foreign ministers, members of royal families and some of the world?s most renowned executives and of course most thousands of Egyptian , Arabian & foreigner locals and expats who have blessed us with their presence.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/25/0e/a0/7d/cover.jpg', 'Fairuz Finest Lebanese Cuisine', '4.5', 'http://www.fairuzrestaurantsharm.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(347, 'Soho Square Sharks Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 12444 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Casual dining from the Red Sea area\'s newest and most diverse fast-food service. Akuna Matata is an array of various ethnic food outlets. Fish & Chips (Fresh Fish Restaurant), Mana Pizza (Pizzeria), Noodles (Chinese noodles), BBQ, Casablanca (Moroccan), La Cantina (Mexican) and Falafel & Egyptian Feteer. It\'s just perfect that suits all the family and everyone else!', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0c/dd/ff/7f/photo1jpg.jpg', 'Akuna Matata', '4.5', 'http://www.soho-sharm.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(348, 'Grand Rotana Resort & Spa 296 Shark\'s Bay, South Sinai, Sharm El Sheikh - Egypt, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Silk Road Restaurant, where Eastern cooking compliments western cuisine, Silk Road is the signature restaurant of the Grand Rotana Resort & Spa with its 3 show kitchens featuring cuisines from China and Thailand passing by India and Arabia to Western Europe. Located in the second floor down the hotel\'s Lobby. Dress Code: Smart Casual. Silk Road is included in the Ultra All Inclusive Formula', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/04/94/90/94/silk-road.jpg', 'Silk Road', '4.5', 'http://www.rotana.com/hoteldiningdesc-15-5-4-96.htm', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(349, 'La Strada Mall Nabq, Sharm El Sheikh 46628 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Experience the ultimate nightlife at Motion Sharm El Sheikh! ??? With our bar, lounge and nightclub, we offer the perfect setting for an unforgettable evening. Enjoy our American casual dining menu, sip on handcrafted cocktails at the bar, and dance the night away to the beats of our talented DJs. Join us for the ultimate fusion of great food, vibrant ambiance, and non-stop fun! ???????', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/29/ea/2a/49/american-casual-dining.jpg', 'Motion Sharm El Sheikh', '5', 'https://motionsharm.com/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(350, 'Gastec station , Old Market Restaurant No.3, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Welcome to My Burger, the premier destination for delicious, juicy, fresh and convenient eat-in and takeaway.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/2a/0e/1d/86/white-sauce-pasta-and.jpg', 'My Burger', '5', 'http://www.myburgeregp.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(351, 'Naama Bay At the Sharm El Sheikh Marriott Resort, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Kona Kai Sushi Bar and Teppanyaki Restaurant offers a creative selection of both Sushi and Teppanyaki using only the finest quality of ingredients available. Our talented Chef\'s create cuisine unsurpassed in it\'s excellence and Kona Kai is proud to have the distinction of being Sharm el Sheikhs original Teppanyaki restaurant. Reservations are recommended for our Sushi Bar and required for our Teppanyaki Dining so please give us a quick call to book and we are, as always, at your service...', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/07/45/e0/60/kona-kai-sushi-bar-restaurant.jpg', 'Kona Kai Sushi Bar & Restaurant', '4.5', 'https://all.accor.com/hotel/B6T1/index.en.shtml', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(352, 'Al Fanar Street Renaissance Sharm El Sheikh Golden View Beach Resort, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Calamari Seafood Market Restaurant is the premiere beach front restaurant in Sharm El Sheikh. Enjoy the sea breeze & sunsets while having your tasty, fresh and healthy dinner from the sea direct to your plate.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/0c/e0/f3/b8/seafood-rice.jpg', 'Calamari Seafood Market Restaurant', '4.5', 'http://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/sshbr-renaissance-sharm-el-sheikh-golden-view-beach-resort/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(353, 'Savoy Hotel Sharm EL Shiekh, Sharm El Sheikh 169 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Soho Square introduces a new and unique style of cuisine to Egypt The Caligula nightclub has been re-launched with a new entertainments concept. The hot rock dining and ballroom dancing! A piece of volcanic rock is heated for over several hours before being brought directly to your table. You then have the pleasure of being able to cook a dinner of your own choosing from a large and varied menu. Ancient cultures have been using this method for thousands of years, it is also very healthy as no oil or fat is used during the process, all the nutrients are sealed within. Hot rock dining is a very relaxed and sociable way to eat. There are no lengthy pauses in conversation when the plates of food are served and everybody \"tucks in\" as you cook the food at your own pace. This ensures that every last piece is hot and fresh. The whole method of dining becomes more leisurely and slower, where everybody tends to pause for conversation far more frequently. Only the freshet cuts of meat and fish are selected, you can choose from such sumptuous delights as Australian loin of lamb, black Angus beef ribs, Cajun salmon steaks, prawn and calamari skewers, plus much more.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/05/38/f3/37/caligula-hot-rock.jpg', 'Caligula Hot Rock', '4.5', 'http://www.soho-sharm.com/sharm-restaurant-Hot-Rock-_-ballroom-dancing', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(354, 'King Of Bahrein Street, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Bus Stop is a well known Egyptian brand since 1987. Here, the menu is specialized in Homemade Burgers with a variety to suit every taste. We air live sports on Giant screen, boast the best pool table in town (upstairs). Let the Good Times Roll', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/2a/3e/c4/8e/brunswick-pool-table.jpg', 'Bus Stop Naama Bay', '5', 'http://busstopegypt.com/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(355, 'Naama Bay, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Restaurant cafe\', young and colored, kind staff all italian style', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/08/5c/5f/11/why-not-esterno.jpg', 'WHY NOT Risto Cafe\'', '5', 'http://www.hardrockcafe.com/location/sharm-el-sheikh/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(356, 'Hilton Sharks Bay Resort Ras Nusrani, Sharks Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 203 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'The Asian fusion restaurant and Teppanyaki grill brings together a host of exotic ingredients, flavors and dishes from across the continent. Savor Chinese, Thai, Indian and Japanese favorites. The Teppanyaki grill is the beating heart of the restaurant, and a centerpiece of food theater. Watching the expert chefs at work is as thrilling as it is delicious.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/05/94/55/94/teppanyaki-grill.jpg', 'House of Asia', '5', 'http://www1.hilton.com/en_US/hi/hotel/SSHSBHI-Hilton-Sharks-Bay-Resort/index.do', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(357, '86 Pyramisa Road, SUNRISE Arabian Beach Resort, Sharm El Sheikh 46628 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Amazing panoramic sea view, Fresh seafood, Free Wifi, Direct on the beach, and Indoor and Outdoor Seating Area', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/17/10/69/b4/felucca-seafood-restaurant.jpg', 'Felucca SeaFood Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.sunrise-resorts.com/Home/SHARM_EL_SHEIKH/SUNRISE_Grand_Select_Arabian_Beach_Resort', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(358, 'Qesm Sharm Ash Sheikh, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Beach bar and restaurant serving freshly cooked food on our beach. With fantastic views of Tiran Island, it is famous for its fresh fish and seafood dishes but also serves a wide range of meat and vegetarian options and desserts. Serving breakfast, lunch and dinner as well as the best sisha in our Bedouin Tent. Perfect for families, friends and couples.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/07/de/81/ca/bedouin-tent.jpg', 'Umbi Restaurant Sharks Bay', '4', 'http://www.sharksbay.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(359, 'Om El Sied Hill, El Fanar st Renaissance Sharm El Sheikh Golden View Beach Resort, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Ristorante La Casa Pizza & Pasta is an authentic Italian Street Restaurant serves freshly hand crafted food in a cozy home setting. Enjoy your all-time favorite Pasta or Pizza dish prepared with passion in front of you.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/11/ee/d9/0e/delightful-pasta-at-la.jpg', 'Ristorante La Casa Pizza & Pasta', '4.5', 'http://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/sshbr-renaissance-sharm-el-sheikh-golden-view-beach-resort/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(360, 'Om El Seed, Sharm El Sheikh, South Sinai, Egypt, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'La Luna an Italian themed restaurant which offers cui-sine from the region in a worm ambient setting, that view of the red sea id truly beautiful and only rivaled by the food a true delight and best of fine dine and with an excellent wine menu. There is also a private room for those celebrating special occasions or looking for an intimate, romantic dinner', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-w/07/e5/b0/a6/la-luna-monte-carlo.jpg', 'La Luna - Monte Carlo', '4.5', 'http://www.montecarloresortsegypt.com', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(361, 'Gardens Bay Park Regency Sharm El Sheikh Resort, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Situated next lazy river pool, a Mediterranean-style … la carte restaurant, offers beverages, snacks, and lunch. Located in Park Regency Sharm El Sheikh Resort.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/18/10/70/9e/cascades-restuarant.jpg', 'Cascades Restaurant & Bar', '4', 'https://www.parkregency.net/restaurants', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(362, 'Grand Rotana Resort & Spa, Sharm El Sheikh 65239 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Offering contemporary Italian cuisine in a fresh colourful surrounds with sweeping views of the swimming pool and Red Sea. Re-creating the ambience of a typical Italian trattoria, Mezzaluna includes both indoor and al fresco dining on an adjoining terrace with a diverse range of Italian wines.Located by the pool.Dress Code: Smart CasualOpening Hours Lunch:12:30noon until 05:00pm and fro', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/15/b9/10/84/mezzaluna.jpg', 'Mezzaluna', '4.5', 'http://www.rotana.com/rotanahotelandresorts/egypt/sharmelsheikh/grandrotanaresortandspa/dining', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(363, 'Salah Taher St. Shores Amphoras Resort, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Bella Vista - Italian RestaurantThis Italian restaurant overlooks the beautiful waterfalls which flow into the sea below. Bella Vista offers a tantalizing selection of Italian specialties cooked and prepared to perfection. Guests can choose from a wide range of traditional antipasti, selection of pastas and pizzas, mouth-watering main courses and delicious desserts.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-s/04/95/27/22/bella-vista-italian-restaurant.jpg', 'Bella Vista Italian Restaurant', '4', 'http://www.shoreshotels.com/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(364, 'Jaz Fanara Resort & Residence, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Nino?s Italian Restaurant offers a dining experience with atmosphere and d‚cor ideally suited to match food and theme. A terrace is also available for a romantic candlelit dinner to experience the Italian ?al fresco? feeling. Our menu is prepared using only the finest & freshest ingredients and includes a number of classic Italian appetizers, mains and desserts. You can enjoy as well a wide selection of alcoholic & non-alcoholic beverages. Two dinner sittings are available. We serve dinner against extra charge and reservation is required in advance. Timings: 6:30 pm? 9 :30 pm', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/28/5b/f3/5f/nino-s-italian-restaurant.jpg', 'Nino\'s Italian Restaurant', '5', 'https://www.jazhotels.com/hoteldetail/4-egypt-sharm-el-sheikh-jaz-fanara-resort', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(365, 'Coast Rd Sharm El Sheikh Marriott Resort, Sharm El Sheikh Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'La cucina piccola fal la casa grande! An Italian proverb that translates as A small kitchen makes the house big. Parmizzano\'s Restaurant offers a mouthwatering array of Classic and Contemporary Italian Cuisine in a stunningly beautiful setting. Both Indoor and Outdoor seating is available and both our highly trained service and culinary team are ready, willing and able to welcome you to one of sharm\'s best kept secrets.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/07/44/cd/48/parmizzano-s.jpg', 'Parmizzano\'s', '4', 'http://www.marriott.com/hotels/hotel-information/restaurant/ssheg-sharm-el-sheikh-marriott-resort/', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
(366, 'Coast Rd M”venpick Resort Sharm el Sheikh, Naama Bay, Sharm El Sheikh 46619 Egypt', 'Sharm El Sheikh', 'Italian Restaurant ?La Brise? is the perfect place for a cozy, quite Italian dinner. Our talented chefs will deliver Italy?s culture at your table,.A taste you will always remember.', 'https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-m/1280/22/76/3f/12/enjoy-a-tasteful-italian.jpg', 'La Brise', '5', 'https://www.movenpick.com/en/africa/egypt/sharm-el-sheikh/resort-sharm-el-sheikh/restaurants/la-brise.html', 44, '2024-05-12 12:22:51', '2024-05-12 12:22:51'),
